{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775873497415,"sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4f1498001qYDC21QCHFViDQ","messageID":"msg_d7a4f063f001W7RCLVNxolgQCs","sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_811b901146e2470cb046068e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n2: \n3: **Module:** manifests\n4: **Language:** YAML\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中，命名风格不一致，且部分组件（如 Volcano scheduler）的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，并确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: - **目录重组：** 将 `rbac-router.yaml` 移入 `templates/rbac/` 目录，重命名为 `router.yaml`\n16: - **Volcano RBAC 抽取：** 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中抽离 RBAC 资源（SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding）至 `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`，原模板保留 ConfigMap/Service/Deployment\n17: - **Values 控制统一：** 为所有 RBAC 资源添加 `values.yaml` 开关：\n18:   - `workloadmanager.rbac.create`（默认 `true`，保持向后兼容）\n19:   - `router.rbac.create`（已存在，默认 `false`）\n20:   - `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create`（默认与 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` 联动）\n21: - **命名规范统一：**\n22:   - ServiceAccount: `<component>` 或 `agentcube-<component>`（与 Deployment 命名一致）\n23:   - ClusterRole/Role: `agentcube-<component>`（添加 `agentcube-` 前缀避免集群命名冲突）\n24:   - ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding: `agentcube-<component>-binding`\n25: - **标签一致性：** 所有 RBAC 资源添加 `app.kubernetes.io/name`, `app.kubernetes.io/instance`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` 标签\n26: - **`_helpers.tpl` 扩展：** 新增 `agentcube.rbacName` 和 `agentcube.rbacBindingName` 模板 helper，统一 RBAC 资源命名逻辑\n27: \n28: ### Out of Scope\n29: \n30: - RBAC 权限范围的变更（不增减任何 apiGroups/resources/verbs）\n31: - 新增组件的 RBAC（如 agentd、picod 的 RBAC 由后续 AR 处理）\n32: - NetworkPolicy 配置\n33: - PodSecurityPolicy / PodSecurityStandards 配置\n34: - 外部 RBAC 集成（如 OPA/Gatekeeper、Kyverno）\n35: \n36: ## Architecture Summary\n37: \n38: **当前状态（Before）：**\n39: \n40: ```\n41: templates/\n42: ├── rbac/\n43: │   └── workloadmanager.yaml      # SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n44: ├── rbac-router.yaml              # SA + Role + RoleBinding (条件渲染)\n45: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment (混合)\n46: ```\n47: \n48: **目标状态（After）：**\n49: \n50: ```\n51: templates/\n52: ├── rbac/\n53: │   ├── workloadmanager.yaml      # SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (不变)\n54: │   ├── router.yaml               # SA + Role + RoleBinding (从 rbac-router.yaml 迁入)\n55: │   └── volcano-scheduler.yaml    # SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (从 volcano 模板抽取)\n56: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # 仅保留 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment\n57: ```\n58: \n59: **RBAC 资源矩阵：**\n60: \n61: | 组件 | ServiceAccount | Role 类型 | 绑定类型 | 条件开关 | 默认值 |\n62: |------|---------------|-----------|---------|---------|--------|\n63: | WorkloadManager | `workloadmanager` | ClusterRole | ClusterRoleBinding | `workloadmanager.rbac.create` | `true` |\n64: | Router | `agentcube-router` | Role (namespace) | RoleBinding | `router.rbac.create` | `false` |\n65: | Volcano Scheduler | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | ClusterRole | ClusterRoleBinding | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` | `{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` |\n66: \n67: **Values 变更：**\n68: \n69: ```yaml\n70: workloadmanager:\n71:   rbac:\n72:     create: true                    # 新增\n73: \n74: router:\n75:   rbac:\n76:     create: false                   # 已存在，保持不变\n77: \n78: volcano:\n79:   scheduler:\n80:     enabled: false\n81:     rbac:\n82:       create: \"\"                    # 新增，空字符串表示跟随 enabled\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ## Impact Analysis\n86: \n87: | Area | Impact |\n88: |------|--------|\n89: | **Consumers** | 现有 `helm install/upgrade` 流程不受影响（WorkloadManager RBAC 默认开启）；使用 `--set router.rbac.create=true` 的用户行为不变 |\n90: | **Backward compatibility** | 文件重命名 (`rbac-router.yaml` → `rbac/router.yaml`) 在 `helm upgrade` 时会被正确处理（Helm 按资源 GVK + namespace + name 追踪，不按文件名）；Volcano RBAC 从混合模板抽取后，已部署的 Volcano 资源不会被删除重建 |\n91: | **Dependencies** | 无新增外部依赖；依赖 AR-030（Helm Chart 模板与 Values）作为基线 |\n92: | **Security** | 不改变任何权限范围；ClusterRole 命名添加 `agentcube-` 前缀降低与集群中其他同名 Role 的冲突风险 |\n93: | **Performance** | 无影响（RBAC 资源数量不变） |\n94: | **Operations** | RBAC 资源集中管理，便于审计和权限审查；`helm template` 输出中 RBAC 资源按组件分文件，可读性提升 |\n95: \n96: ## Alternatives Considered\n97: \n98: | Alternative | Pros | Cons | Decision |\n99: |-------------|------|------|----------|\n100: | **保持现状，仅添加注释** | 零风险，无需改动 | RBAC 分散问题未解决，新成员难以定位所有权限定义 | Rejected — 不解决根本问题 |\n101: | **全部 RBAC 合并为单个文件 `rbac/all.yaml`** | 单一文件便于审计 | 文件过大，条件渲染逻辑复杂，diff 不友好 | Rejected — 按组件分文件更利于维护和 code review |\n102: | **使用 Helm library chart 封装 RBAC** | 可复用，支持参数化 | 增加复杂度，对当前 3 个组件来说过度设计 | Rejected — 当前规模下简单模板即可满足 |\n103: | **引入 `rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1` Aggregated ClusterRole** | 可通过 label selector 动态组合权限 | Kubernetes 1.28+ 支持有限，增加理解成本，AgentCube 权限边界明确无需聚合 | Rejected — 权限集合固定且明确，无需动态聚合 |\n104: | **本方案（目录重组 + Values 统一）** | 结构清晰，向后兼容，易于扩展新组件 | 需要文件移动和少量模板重构 | **Accepted** — 在复杂度和收益之间取得最佳平衡 |\n105: \n106: ## Upstream Dependencies\n107: \n108: - AR-030（Helm Chart 模板与 Values）— 本变更在其建立的 chart 结构上进行调整\n109: - Kubernetes RBAC API `rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1`\n110: - Helm 3（资源追踪和生命周期管理）\n111: \n112: ## Status\n113: \n114: - [ ] Proposal review\n115: - [ ] Implementation\n116: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 116 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n**Module:** manifests\n**Language:** YAML\n**Size:** M\n\n## Purpose\n\n统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中，命名风格不一致，且部分组件（如 Volcano scheduler）的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，并确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n- **目录重组：** 将 `rbac-router.yaml` 移入 `templates/rbac/` 目录，重命名为 `router.yaml`\n- **Volcano RBAC 抽取：** 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中抽离 RBAC 资源（SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding）至 `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`，原模板保留 ConfigMap/Service/Deployment\n- **Values 控制统一：** 为所有 RBAC 资源添加 `values.yaml` 开关：\n  - `workloadmanager.rbac.create`（默认 `true`，保持向后兼容）\n  - `router.rbac.create`（已存在，默认 `false`）\n  - `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create`（默认与 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` 联动）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775873497406,"end":1775873497413}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775873498747,"sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4f19cd0015hYCyREDO8m9jg","messageID":"msg_d7a4f063f001W7RCLVNxolgQCs","sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c0878dd631fb42f88557d465","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Design/设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n6: \n7: 本变更统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中（`rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`、`rbac-router.yaml`、`volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`），命名风格不一致，且 Volcano 调度器的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。\n8: \n9: 本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。这是 RBAC 配置的基础设施重构，不改变任何权限范围。\n10: \n11: ### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n12: \n13: **当前状态 (Before):**\n14: \n15: ```\n16: manifests/charts/base/templates/\n17: ├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service\n18: ├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service\n19: ├── rbac/\n20: │   └── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (无 values gate)\n21: ├── rbac-router.yaml                      # Router SA + Role + RoleBinding (条件渲染)\n22: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment (混合)\n23: ```\n24: \n25: **目标状态 (After):**\n26: \n27: ```\n28: manifests/charts/base/templates/\n29: ├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service (不变)\n30: ├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service (不变)\n31: ├── rbac/\n32: │   ├── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (添加 values gate + 重命名)\n33: │   ├── router.yaml                       # Router SA + Role + RoleBinding (从 rbac-router.yaml 迁入)\n34: │   └── volcano-scheduler.yaml            # SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (从 volcano 模板抽取)\n35: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # 仅保留 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment\n36: ```\n37: \n38: ### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n39: \n40: ```\n41: AR-031 RBAC 配置\n42:   ├── 前置依赖\n43:   │   ├── AR-030 (Helm Chart 模板与 Values)     # 基线 chart 结构\n44:   │   ├── Kubernetes RBAC API v1                # rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n45:   │   └── Helm 3                                # 资源追踪和生命周期管理\n46:   │\n47:   ├── 模板渲染依赖\n48:   │   ├── _helpers.tpl                          # agentcube.rbacName, agentcube.rbacBindingName\n49:   │   └── values.yaml                           # workloadmanager.rbac.create, router.rbac.create, volcano.scheduler.rbac.create\n50:   │\n51:   └── 验证工具\n52:       ├── helm lint                             # 模板语法和结构验证\n53:       ├── helm template                         # 渲染结果验证\n54:       └── kubectl apply --dry-run=client        # Kubernetes 资源有效性验证\n55: ```\n56: \n57: ### 1.4 RBAC 资源矩阵 (RBAC Resource Matrix)\n58: \n59: | 组件 | ServiceAccount | Role 类型 | Role 名称 | 绑定类型 | 绑定名称 | 条件开关 | 默认值 |\n60: |------|---------------|-----------|-----------|---------|---------|---------|--------|\n61: | WorkloadManager | `workloadmanager` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-workloadmanager` | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | `workloadmanager.rbac.create` | `true` |\n62: | Router | `agentcube-router` (或自定义) | Role (namespace) | `agentcube-router` | RoleBinding | `agentcube-router-binding` | `router.rbac.create` | `false` |\n63: | Volcano Scheduler | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` | 跟随 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n64: \n65: ### 1.5 命名规范 (Naming Convention)\n66: \n67: | 资源类型 | 命名规则 | 示例 | 说明 |\n68: |----------|---------|------|------|\n69: | ServiceAccount | `<component>` 或 `agentcube-<component>` | `workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router` | 与 Deployment 命名保持一致，不添加额外前缀 |\n70: | ClusterRole/Role | `agentcube-<component>` | `agentcube-workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router` | 添加 `agentcube-` 前缀避免集群级命名冲突 |\n71: | ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding | `agentcube-<component>-binding` | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | 添加 `agentcube-` 前缀和 `-binding` 后缀 |\n72: \n73: 名称长度限制：Kubernetes 资源名称最大 63 字符。`_helpers.tpl` 中的 helper 函数 SHALL 对超长名称进行 `trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\"` 处理。\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n78: \n79: ### 2.1 values.yaml RBAC 键树\n80: \n81: ```yaml\n82: workloadmanager:\n83:   rbac:\n84:     create: true                    # 新增: 控制 WM RBAC 资源渲染, 默认 true 保持向后兼容\n85: \n86: router:\n87:   rbac:\n88:     create: false                   # 已存在: 控制 Router RBAC 资源渲染, 默认 false\n89:   serviceAccountName: \"\"            # 已存在: 自定义 SA 名称 (影响 Router RBAC 资源命名)\n90: \n91: volcano:\n92:   scheduler:\n93:     enabled: false                  # 已存在: 控制 Volcano 调度器整体渲染\n94:     rbac:\n95:       create: \"\"                    # 新增: 空字符串表示跟随 enabled; 显式 true/false 覆盖\n96: ```\n97: \n98: ### 2.2 values.yaml 键树关系图 (RBAC 部分)\n99: \n100: ```\n101: values.yaml\n102: ├── workloadmanager\n103: │   └── rbac\n104: │       └── create: true            # 新增: WM RBAC 开关\n105: ├── router\n106: │   ├── serviceAccountName: \"\"      # 已存在: 自定义 SA 名称\n107: │   └── rbac\n108: │       └── create: false           # 已存在: Router RBAC 开关\n109: └── volcano\n110:     └── scheduler\n111:         ├── enabled: false          # 已存在: Volcano 总开关\n112:         └── rbac\n113:             └── create: \"\"          # 新增: Volcano RBAC 开关 (空=跟随 enabled)\n114: ```\n115: \n116: ### 2.3 RBAC 标签规范 (Label Schema)\n117: \n118: 所有 RBAC 资源 (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, Role, ClusterRoleBinding, RoleBinding) 的 `metadata.labels` SHALL 包含以下标签：\n119: \n120: | 标签键 | 值 | 来源 | 说明 |\n121: |--------|-----|------|------|\n122: | `app.kubernetes.io/name` | `<component-name>` | 组件名称 | `workloadmanager`, `router`, `volcano-scheduler` |\n123: | `app.kubernetes.io/instance` | `{{ .Release.Name }}` | Helm Release 名称 | 区分同一集群中的不同 release |\n124: | `app.kubernetes.io/component` | `rbac` | 硬编码 | 标识资源类型为 RBAC |\n125: | `helm.sh/chart` | `{{ include \"agentcube.chart\" . }}` | `_helpers.tpl` | Chart 版本标识 |\n126: | `app.kubernetes.io/managed-by` | `{{ .Release.Service }}` | Helm | 管理工具标识 |\n127: | `app.kubernetes.io/version` | `{{ .Chart.AppVersion }}` | Chart.yaml | 应用版本 (如果定义了) |\n128: \n129: 其中 `app.kubernetes.io/name` 的值在 RBAC 资源中为组件名 (而非 chart 名)，通过以下方式注入：\n130: \n131: ```yaml\n132: app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ .componentName }}\n133: ```\n134: \n135: 其中 `.componentName` 在各模板中通过 `$_ := set . \"componentName\" \"<name>\"` 方式设置。\n136: \n137: ### 2.4 _helpers.tpl 新增 RBAC 辅助函数\n138: \n139: ```\n140: agentcube.rbacName\n141:   输入: component name (string)\n142:   输出: \"agentcube-<component>\" (截断至 63 字符, 去除尾部 -)\n143:   用途: ClusterRole/Role 名称生成\n144: \n145: agentcube.rbacBindingName\n146:   输入: component name (string)\n147:   输出: \"agentcube-<component>-binding\" (截断至 63 字符, 去除尾部 -)\n148:   用途: ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding 名称生成\n149: ```\n150: \n151: **Helper 实现:**\n152: \n153: ```go\n154: {{/*\n155: Generate RBAC resource name with agentcube- prefix.\n156: Usage: include \"agentcube.rbacName\" \"workloadmanager\"\n157: */}}\n158: {{- define \"agentcube.rbacName\" -}}\n159: {{- printf \"agentcube-%s\" . | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n160: {{- end }}\n161: \n162: {{/*\n163: Generate RBAC binding name with agentcube- prefix and -binding suffix.\n164: Usage: include \"agentcube.rbacBindingName\" \"workloadmanager\"\n165: */}}\n166: {{- define \"agentcube.rbacBindingName\" -}}\n167: {{- printf \"agentcube-%s-binding\" . | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n168: {{- end }}\n169: ```\n170: \n171: ### 2.5 RBAC 权限规则 (保持不变)\n172: \n173: 权限规则与变更前完全一致，仅资源名称和文件位置变化。\n174: \n175: #### 2.5.1 WorkloadManager ClusterRole 规则\n176: \n177: | apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n178: |-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n179: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | agent-sandbox 沙箱管理 |\n180: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱声明 |\n181: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxtemplates` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱模板 |\n182: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱预热池 |\n183: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools/status` | `get,update,patch` | 预热池状态 |\n184: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n185: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/status` | `get,update,patch` | CodeInterpreter 状态 |\n186: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/finalizers` | `update` | CodeInterpreter finalizer |\n187: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes` | `get,list,watch` | AgentRuntime CRD (只读) |\n188: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes/status` | `update,patch` | AgentRuntime 状态 |\n189: | `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch` | Pod 查询 |\n190: | `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | Secret 管理 |\n191: | `authentication.k8s.io` | `tokenreviews` | `create` | 认证 Token 审查 |\n192: \n193: #### 2.5.2 Router Role 规则\n194: \n195: | apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n196: |-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n197: | `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 命名空间级 Secret 管理 |\n198: \n199: #### 2.5.3 Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole 规则\n200: \n201: | apiGroups | resources | verbs |\n202: |-----------|-----------|-------|\n203: | `apiextensions.k8s.io` | `customresourcedefinitions` | `create,get,list,watch,delete` |\n204: | `\"\"` | `events` | `create,list,watch,update,patch` |\n205: | `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch,patch,delete` |\n206: | `\"\"` | `pods/status` | `update` |\n207: | `\"\"` | `pods/binding` | `create` |\n208: | `\"\"` | `persistentvolumeclaims` | `list,watch,update` |\n209: | `\"\"` | `persistentvolumes` | `list,watch,update` |\n210: | `\"\"` | `namespaces,services,replicationcontrollers` | `list,watch,get` |\n211: | `\"\"` | `resourcequotas` | `list,watch` |\n212: | `\"\"` | `nodes` | `get,list,watch,update,patch` |\n213: | `storage.k8s.io` | `storageclasses,csinodes,csidrivers,csistoragecapacities,volumeattachments` | `list,watch` |\n214: | `policy` | `poddisruptionbudgets` | `list,watch` |\n215: | `scheduling.k8s.io` | `priorityclasses` | `get,list,watch` |\n216: | `scheduling.incubator.k8s.io`, `scheduling.volcano.sh` | `podgroups` | `list,watch,update` |\n217: | `\"\"` | `configmaps` | `get,list,watch,create,delete,update` |\n218: | `apps` | `daemonsets,replicasets,statefulsets` | `list,watch,get` |\n219: | `coordination.k8s.io` | `leases` | `get,create,update,watch` |\n220: | `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch` |\n221: | `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims/status` | `update` |\n222: | `resource.k8s.io` | `deviceclasses,resourceslices` | `get,list,watch,create` |\n223: | `shard.volcano.sh` | `nodeshards` | `list,watch,get,update` |\n224: \n225: ---\n226: \n227: ## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n228: \n229: ### 3.1 模板渲染契约 (Template Rendering Contracts)\n230: \n231: #### 3.1.1 WorkloadManager RBAC 模板\n232: \n233: 文件: `templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\n234: \n235: 条件: `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}`\n236: \n237: 渲染产物:\n238: \n239: | 资源 | 名称 | 命名空间 |\n240: |------|------|----------|\n241: | ServiceAccount | `workloadmanager` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n242: | ClusterRole | `agentcube-workloadmanager` | 集群级 (无 namespace) |\n243: | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | 集群级 (无 namespace) |\n244: \n245: ClusterRoleBinding 引用关系:\n246: ```yaml\n247: roleRef:\n248:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n249:   kind: ClusterRole\n250:   name: agentcube-workloadmanager\n251: subjects:\n252:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n253:     name: workloadmanager\n254:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n255: ```\n256: \n257: #### 3.1.2 Router RBAC 模板\n258: \n259: 文件: `templates/rbac/router.yaml`\n260: \n261: 条件: `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}`\n262: \n263: SA 名称解析: `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}`\n264: \n265: 渲染产物:\n266: \n267: | 资源 | 名称 | 命名空间 |\n268: |------|------|----------|\n269: | ServiceAccount | `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName \\| default \"agentcube-router\" }}` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n270: | Role | `agentcube-router` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n271: | RoleBinding | `agentcube-router-binding` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n272: \n273: RoleBinding 引用关系:\n274: ```yaml\n275: roleRef:\n276:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n277:   kind: Role\n278:   name: agentcube-router\n279: subjects:\n280:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n281:     name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n282:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n283: ```\n284: \n285: **注意:** Router Role 名称固定为 `agentcube-router`，不跟随 `serviceAccountName` 变化。这与变更前行为一致（变更前 Role 名称也使用 `serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\"`，而默认值就是 `agentcube-router`，变更后统一为固定名称）。\n286: \n287: #### 3.1.3 Volcano Scheduler RBAC 模板\n288: \n289: 文件: `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n290: \n291: 条件: `{{- if or .Values.volcano.scheduler.rbac.create .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}`\n292: \n293: 渲染产物:\n294: \n295: | 资源 | 名称 | 命名空间 |\n296: |------|------|----------|\n297: | ServiceAccount | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n298: | ClusterRole | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | 集群级 (无 namespace) |\n299: | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | 集群级 (无 namespace) |\n300: \n301: ClusterRoleBinding 引用关系:\n302: ```yaml\n303: roleRef:\n304:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n305:   kind: ClusterRole\n306:   name: agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler\n307: subjects:\n308:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n309:     name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n310:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n311: ```\n312: \n313: ### 3.2 条件渲染逻辑 (Conditional Rendering Logic)\n314: \n315: | 模板 | 条件表达式 | 行为 |\n316: |------|-----------|------|\n317: | `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}` | `true` 时渲染, `false` 时跳过 |\n318: | `rbac/router.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}` | `true` 时渲染, `false` 时跳过 |\n319: | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | `{{- if or .Values.volcano.scheduler.rbac.create .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` | 任一为 true 时渲染 |\n320: | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` | 仅渲染 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment |\n321: \n322: **Volcano RBAC 条件逻辑详解:**\n323: \n324: ```\n325: volcano.scheduler.rbac.create  | volcano.scheduler.enabled | 渲染 RBAC?\n326: -------------------------------|---------------------------|------------\n327: \"\" (空/未设置)                  | false                     | 否 (两者都 falsy)\n328: \"\" (空/未设置)                  | true                      | 是 (enabled 为 true)\n329: true                           | false                     | 是 (rbac.create 为 true)\n330: true                           | true                      | 是 (两者都为 true)\n331: false                          | false                     | 否 (rbac.create 显式 false)\n332: false                          | true                      | 否 (rbac.create 显式 false 覆盖)\n333: ```\n334: \n335: ### 3.3 绑定完整性保证 (Binding Integrity Guarantee)\n336: \n337: 每个 Binding 必须正确引用对应的 Role 和 ServiceAccount：\n338: \n339: | Binding | roleRef.kind | roleRef.name | subjects[0].kind | subjects[0].name | subjects[0].namespace |\n340: |---------|-------------|--------------|------------------|------------------|----------------------|\n341: | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-workloadmanager` | ServiceAccount | `workloadmanager` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n342: | `agentcube-router-binding` | Role | `agentcube-router` | ServiceAccount | `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName \\| default \"agentcube-router\" }}` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n343: | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | ServiceAccount | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n344: \n345: ### 3.4 标签注入契约 (Label Injection Contract)\n346: \n347: 所有 RBAC 资源的 `metadata.labels` 通过以下方式注入：\n348: \n349: ```yaml\n350: metadata:\n351:   labels:\n352:     {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\n353:     app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ .componentName }}\n354:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n355: ```\n356: \n357: 其中 `.componentName` 在各模板顶部设置：\n358: \n359: ```yaml\n360: {{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"workloadmanager\" }}    # workloadmanager.yaml\n361: {{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"router\" }}              # router.yaml\n362: {{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"volcano-scheduler\" }}   # volcano-scheduler.yaml\n363: ```\n364: \n365: ### 3.5 Volcano 模板拆分契约 (Volcano Template Split Contract)\n366: \n367: `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 拆分后：\n368: \n369: | 资源 | 归属模板 | 条件 |\n370: |------|---------|------|\n371: | ServiceAccount `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 或 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n372: | ConfigMap `volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap` | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n373: | ClusterRole `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 或 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n374: | ClusterRoleBinding `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 或 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n375: | Service `volcano-agent-scheduler-service` | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n376: | Deployment `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n377: \n378: 拆分后，`volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中 Deployment 的 `serviceAccountName` 仍引用 `volcano-agent-scheduler`，与 RBAC 模板创建的 SA 名称一致。\n379: \n380: ---\n381: \n382: ## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n383: \n384: ### 4.1 模板渲染错误 (Template Rendering Errors)\n385: \n386: | 场景 | 表现 | 处理方式 |\n387: |------|------|----------|\n388: | `values.yaml` 语法错误 | `helm template` 报 YAML parse error | 安装前通过 `helm lint` 捕获 |\n389: | 模板语法错误 (如 `{{- if` 缺少 `{{- end }}`) | `helm template` 报 template rendering failed | 开发阶段通过 `helm template` dry-run 发现 |\n390: | RBAC helper 调用参数错误 | `helm template` 报 template execution error | 确保 helper 调用传入字符串参数 |\n391: | 类型不匹配 (如 `rbac.create` 设为非布尔值) | Helm 条件判断行为不确定 | `values.yaml` 使用正确类型；`helm lint` 可检测部分问题 |\n392: \n393: ### 4.2 Helm 升级迁移场景 (Helm Upgrade Migration)\n394: \n395: #### 4.2.1 WorkloadManager 重命名迁移\n396: \n397: | 资源 | 旧名称 | 新名称 | 迁移行为 |\n398: |------|--------|--------|----------|\n399: | ClusterRole | `workloadmanager` | `agentcube-workloadmanager` | Helm 删除旧资源，创建新资源 |\n400: | ClusterRoleBinding | `workloadmanager` | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | Helm 删除旧资源，创建新资源 |\n401: | ServiceAccount | `workloadmanager` | `workloadmanager` | 名称不变，Helm 原地更新 (仅添加标签) |\n402: \n403: **影响分析:**\n404: - ClusterRole 重命名期间，旧的 ClusterRole 被删除、新的被创建。由于 ClusterRole 是声明式资源，删除和重建之间可能存在短暂窗口期，但 WorkloadManager Pod 不会重启（Deployment 未变更）。\n405: - 在旧 ClusterRole 删除后、新 ClusterRole 创建前的窗口期内，WorkloadManager Pod 的 API 请求可能被拒绝。但由于 Helm 按顺序应用资源，窗口期极短（通常 < 1 秒）。\n406: - 如果集群使用严格的 RBAC 审计策略，可能在审计日志中看到短暂的 `forbidden` 记录。\n407: \n408: #### 4.2.2 Router RBAC 文件移动\n409: \n410: | 资源 | 旧模板文件 | 新模板文件 | 迁移行为 |\n411: |------|-----------|-----------|----------|\n412: | ServiceAccount | `rbac-router.yaml` | `rbac/router.yaml` | Helm 按 GVK+name 追踪，不受文件名影响 |\n413: | Role | `rbac-router.yaml` | `rbac/router.yaml` | 同上 (名称从 `serviceAccountName | default` 变为固定 `agentcube-router`) |\n414: | RoleBinding | `rbac-router.yaml` | `rbac/router.yaml` | 同上 (名称从 `serviceAccountName | default` 变为固定 `agentcube-router-binding`) |\n415: \n416: **注意:** 如果用户之前设置了 `router.serviceAccountName` 为非默认值（如 `my-custom-sa`），则 Role 和 RoleBinding 的旧名称为 `my-custom-sa`，新名称为 `agentcube-router` 和 `agentcube-router-binding`。这会导致 Helm 删除旧资源并创建新资源。\n417: \n418: **缓解措施:** 在 proposal 中已明确 Router Role/RoleBinding 名称统一为 `agentcube-router` 和 `agentcube-router-binding`，不再跟随 `serviceAccountName`。这简化了命名逻辑，但对已使用自定义 SA 名称的用户是一次破坏性变更。由于 `router.rbac.create` 默认值为 `false`，受影响用户极少。\n419: \n420: #### 4.2.3 Volcano RBAC 抽取\n421: \n422: | 资源 | 旧模板文件 | 新模板文件 | 迁移行为 |\n423: |------|-----------|-----------|----------|\n424: | ServiceAccount | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | Helm 按 GVK+name 追踪，不受影响 |\n425: | ClusterRole | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 名称从 `volcano-agent-scheduler` 变为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`，Helm 删除旧创建新 |\n426: | ClusterRoleBinding | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 名称从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-role` 变为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`，Helm 删除旧创建新 |\n427: \n428: **影响分析:**\n429: - Volcano 默认 `enabled: false`，大多数用户不受影响。\n430: - 已启用 Volcano 的用户在升级时，ClusterRole 和 ClusterRoleBinding 会被重建。Volcano Pod 不会重启（Deployment 未变更），但 RBAC 重建期间可能存在短暂权限窗口。\n431: \n432: ### 4.3 权限范围保护 (Permission Scope Preservation)\n433: \n434: | 风险 | 保障措施 |\n435: |------|----------|\n436: | 意外增减权限 | delta-spec 中明确要求权限规则不变；通过 `helm template` 对比变更前后的规则集 |\n437: | 绑定引用错误 | 每个 Binding 的 roleRef 和 subjects 在模板中硬编码，不依赖动态计算 |\n438: | 命名冲突 | ClusterRole 添加 `agentcube-` 前缀，降低与集群中其他同名 Role 的冲突风险 |\n439: \n440: ### 4.4 边界情况处理 (Edge Case Handling)\n441: \n442: | 场景 | 处理 |\n443: |------|------|\n444: | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 设为空字符串 `\"\"` | Helm 模板中 `or \"\" false` 为 falsy，不渲染 RBAC；`or \"\" true` 为 truthy，渲染 RBAC |\n445: | `workloadmanager.rbac.create` 设为 `false` | WM RBAC 资源不渲染；WM Deployment 仍存在但无 SA 关联（使用 default SA） |\n446: | `router.rbac.create` 为 `true` 但 `router.serviceAccountName` 为空 | SA 名称为 `agentcube-router`；Role 名称为 `agentcube-router`；RoleBinding 名称为 `agentcube-router-binding` |\n447: | 组件名称超长 (> 63 字符) | helper 函数 `trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\"` 自动截断 |\n448: \n449: ---\n450: \n451: ## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n452: \n453: ### 5.1 静态验证 (Static Validation)\n454: \n455: #### 5.1.1 Helm Lint\n456: \n457: ```bash\n458: # 默认值 lint\n459: helm lint manifests/charts/base\n460: \n461: # 全量 RBAC 启用 lint\n462: helm lint manifests/charts/base \\\n463:   --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n464:   --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true\n465: ```\n466: \n467: 预期输出：无 errors，允许 warnings（如 `icon` 字段缺失）。\n468: \n469: #### 5.1.2 YAML 语法验证\n470: \n471: ```bash\n472: # 验证 values.yaml 为合法 YAML\n473: python3 -c \"import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml'))\"\n474: ```\n475: \n476: ### 5.2 模板渲染测试 (Template Rendering Tests)\n477: \n478: #### 5.2.1 默认值渲染\n479: \n480: ```bash\n481: # 验证默认模板输出\n482: helm template test manifests/charts/base\n483: ```\n484: \n485: | 断言 | 期望值 |\n486: |------|--------|\n487: | ClusterRole 数量 | 1 (`agentcube-workloadmanager`) |\n488: | ClusterRoleBinding 数量 | 1 (`agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`) |\n489: | ServiceAccount 数量 | 1 (`workloadmanager`) |\n490: | Router RBAC 资源 | 无 (默认关闭) |\n491: | Volcano RBAC 资源 | 无 (默认关闭) |\n492: \n493: #### 5.2.2 关键场景渲染验证\n494: \n495: | 场景 | 命令 | 断言 |\n496: |------|------|------|\n497: | WM RBAC 默认开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 输出含 `kind: ClusterRole` 且 `name: agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n498: | WM RBAC 显式关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false` | 无 WM SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding |\n499: | WM RBAC 显式开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.rbac.create=true` | 输出含 WM 全部三个 RBAC 资源 |\n500: | Router RBAC 关闭 (默认) | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Router SA/Role/RoleBinding |\n501: | Router RBAC 开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true` | 输出含 `kind: Role` 且 `name: agentcube-router` |\n502: | Router RBAC 自定义 SA | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa` | SA 名称为 `my-router-sa`；Role 名称仍为 `agentcube-router` |\n503: | Volcano RBAC 跟随 enabled (false) | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Volcano RBAC 资源 |\n504: | Volcano RBAC 跟随 enabled (true) | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | 输出含 Volcano SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding |\n505: | Volcano RBAC 显式关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` | 无 Volcano RBAC 资源 |\n506: | Volcano RBAC 显式开启 (覆盖 disabled) | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true` | 输出含 Volcano RBAC 资源 |\n507: | WM ClusterRole 规则不变 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | 规则集与变更前一致 (13 条规则) |\n508: | Router Role 规则不变 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true -s templates/rbac/router.yaml` | 规则: secrets 全权限 |\n509: | Volcano ClusterRole 规则不变 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 规则集与变更前一致 (18 条规则) |\n510: \n511: #### 5.2.3 标签验证\n512: \n513: ```bash\n514: # 验证 WM RBAC 资源标签\n515: helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml | \\\n516:   grep -A 5 \"labels:\"\n517: ```\n518: \n519: | 资源 | 期望标签 |\n520: |------|---------|\n521: | ServiceAccount/workloadmanager | `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager`, `app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` |\n522: | ClusterRole/agentcube-workloadmanager | `app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` |\n523: | ClusterRoleBinding/agentcube-workloadmanager-binding | `app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` |\n524: \n525: #### 5.2.4 绑定完整性验证\n526: \n527: ```bash\n528: # 验证 WM ClusterRoleBinding 引用关系\n529: helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml | \\\n530:   grep -A 10 \"kind: ClusterRoleBinding\"\n531: ```\n532: \n533: | 断言 | 期望值 |\n534: |------|--------|\n535: | `roleRef.name` | `agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n536: | `subjects[0].name` | `workloadmanager` |\n537: | `subjects[0].namespace` | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` (渲染后为 release 命名空间) |\n538: \n539: ### 5.3 Kubernetes 验证 (Dry-Run)\n540: \n541: ```bash\n542: # 默认值 dry-run\n543: helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n544: \n545: # 全量 RBAC 启用 dry-run\n546: helm template test manifests/charts/base \\\n547:   --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n548:   --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\\n549:   | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n550: ```\n551: \n552: ### 5.4 升级向后兼容性测试 (Upgrade Backward Compatibility)\n553: \n554: ```bash\n555: # 1. 使用变更前 chart 安装\n556: helm install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace\n557: \n558: # 2. 验证旧资源存在\n559: kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager\n560: kubectl get clusterrolebinding workloadmanager\n561: \n562: # 3. 使用变更后 chart 升级\n563: helm upgrade agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube\n564: \n565: # 4. 验证新资源存在，旧资源已删除\n566: kubectl get clusterrole agentcube-workloadmanager\n567: kubectl get clusterrolebinding agentcube-workloadmanager-binding\n568: kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager  # 应不存在\n569: \n570: # 5. 验证 WM Pod 未重启\n571: kubectl get pods -n agentcube -l app=workloadmanager -o jsonpath='{.items[0].status.containerStatuses[0].restartCount}'\n572: # 期望: 0\n573: ```\n574: \n575: ### 5.5 测试场景覆盖矩阵 (Test Scenario Coverage Matrix)\n576: \n577: | Delta Spec 场景 | 测试方法 | 验证点 |\n578: |-----------------|----------|--------|\n579: | RBAC files in correct directory | 目录检查 | `rbac/` 包含 `workloadmanager.yaml`, `router.yaml`, `volcano-scheduler.yaml` |\n580: | Volcano template retains non-RBAC | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | 仅含 ConfigMap, Service, Deployment |\n581: | Volcano RBAC from new location | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | RBAC 资源出现在输出中 |\n582: | WM RBAC enabled by default | `helm template` | SA + CR + CRB 存在 |\n583: | WM RBAC explicitly disabled | `helm template --set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false` | 无 WM RBAC 资源 |\n584: | WM RBAC explicitly enabled | `helm template --set workloadmanager.rbac.create=true` | SA + CR + CRB 存在 |\n585: | Volcano RBAC follows enabled (false) | `helm template` | 无 Volcano RBAC |\n586: | Volcano RBAC follows enabled (true) | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | SA + CR + CRB 存在 |\n587: | Volcano RBAC explicitly disabled | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` | 无 Volcano RBAC |\n588: | Volcano RBAC explicitly enabled (override) | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true` | SA + CR + CRB 存在 |\n589: | Router RBAC off by default | `helm template` | 无 Router RBAC |\n590: | Router RBAC enabled | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true` | SA + Role + RoleBinding 存在，名称和规则不变 |\n591: | WM ClusterRole has agentcube- prefix | `helm template` | ClusterRole name: `agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n592: | Volcano ClusterRole has agentcube- prefix | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | ClusterRole name: `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` |\n593: | CRB references prefixed CR name | `helm template` | CRB roleRef.name: `agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n594: | WM binding has -binding suffix | `helm template` | CRB name: `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` |\n595: | Router binding has -binding suffix | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true` | RB name: `agentcube-router-binding` |\n596: | Volcano binding has -binding suffix | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | CRB name: `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` |\n597: | WM SA name unchanged | `helm template` | SA name: `workloadmanager` |\n598: | Router SA respects serviceAccountName | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa` | SA name: `my-router-sa` |\n599: | Volcano SA name unchanged | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | SA name: `volcano-agent-scheduler` |\n600: | WM ClusterRole rules preserved | `helm template -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | 13 条规则完整 |\n601: | Router Role rules preserved | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true -s templates/rbac/router.yaml` | secrets 全权限 |\n602: | Volcano ClusterRole rules preserved | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 18 条规则完整 |\n603: | WM RBAC has k8s standard labels | `helm template -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | 三个标签存在 |\n604: | Router RBAC has k8s standard labels | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true -s templates/rbac/router.yaml` | 三个标签存在 |\n605: | Volcano RBAC has k8s standard labels | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 三个标签存在 |\n606: | rbacName helper generates prefixed name | 模板渲染 | `agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n607: | rbacBindingName helper generates binding name | 模板渲染 | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` |\n608: | Long component names truncated | 模板渲染 (模拟超长名称) | 截断至 63 字符 |\n609: | values.yaml parses with new RBAC keys | YAML parse | 三个 RBAC key 存在且值正确 |\n610: | RBAC key comments document behavior | 文件检查 | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 附近有注释 |\n611: | Upgrade from pre-AR-031 release | `helm upgrade` | 旧 CR 删除，新 CR 创建，Pod 未重启 |\n612: | Router RBAC file move transparent | `helm upgrade` (with router.rbac.create=true) | RBAC 资源未删除重建 |\n613: | WM binding integrity | `helm template` | roleRef + subjects 正确 |\n614: | Router binding integrity | `helm template --set router.rbac.create=true` | roleRef + subjects 正确 |\n615: | Volcano binding integrity | `helm template --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | roleRef + subjects 正确 |\n616: | Helm lint passes (default) | `helm lint` | 无 errors |\n617: | Helm lint passes (all RBAC enabled) | `helm lint --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | 无 errors |\n618: \n619: ---\n620: \n621: ## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n622: \n623: ### 6.1 文件变更顺序\n624: \n625: | 步骤 | 操作 | 文件 | 说明 | 前置依赖 |\n626: |------|------|------|------|----------|\n627: | 1 | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | 添加 `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true` 和 `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create: \"\"` | 无 |\n628: | 2 | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` | 添加 `agentcube.rbacName` 和 `agentcube.rbacBindingName` helper | 步骤 1 |\n629: | 3 | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | 添加 values gate；重命名 CR 为 `agentcube-workloadmanager`；重命名 CRB 为 `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`；添加 k8s 标准标签 | 步骤 2 |\n630: | 4 | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/router.yaml` | 从 `rbac-router.yaml` 复制内容；重命名 Role 为 `agentcube-router`；重命名 RB 为 `agentcube-router-binding`；添加 k8s 标准标签 | 步骤 2 |\n631: | 5 | Delete | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | 已被 `rbac/router.yaml` 替代 | 步骤 4 |\n632: | 6 | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 抽取 SA/CR/CRB；重命名 CR 为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`；重命名 CRB 为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`；添加 values gate；添加 k8s 标准标签 | 步骤 2 |\n633: | 7 | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | 移除 SA/CR/CRB 块；保留 ConfigMap/Service/Deployment | 步骤 6 |\n634: \n635: ### 6.2 并行化分组 (Parallelizable Groups)\n636: \n637: | 组 | 任务 | 说明 |\n638: |----|------|------|\n639: | G1 | 步骤 1 (values.yaml) | 独立修改，无依赖 |\n640: | G2 | 步骤 2 (_helpers.tpl) | 依赖 G1 (目录结构不变，仅添加 helper) |\n641: | G3 | 步骤 3, 4, 6 (三个 RBAC 模板) | 可并行，都依赖 G2 (helper 已定义) |\n642: | G4 | 步骤 5, 7 (删除旧文件 + 修改 Volcano 模板) | 依赖 G3 完成 (新模板已就位) |\n643: \n644: ### 6.3 验证检查清单 (Verification Checklist)\n645: \n646: - [ ] `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors\n647: - [ ] `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 无 errors\n648: - [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 输出合法 YAML\n649: - [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n650: - [ ] `values.yaml` 包含 `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true`\n651: - [ ] `values.yaml` 包含 `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create: \"\"` (空字符串)\n652: - [ ] `values.yaml` 中 `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` 附近有注释说明空字符串行为\n653: - [ ] `_helpers.tpl` 包含 `agentcube.rbacName` helper\n654: - [ ] `_helpers.tpl` 包含 `agentcube.rbacBindingName` helper\n655: - [ ] `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 有 `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}` gate\n656: - [ ] `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 中 ClusterRole 名称为 `agentcube-workloadmanager`\n657: - [ ] `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 中 ClusterRoleBinding 名称为 `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`\n658: - [ ] `rbac/router.yaml` 存在且内容正确\n659: - [ ] `rbac/router.yaml` 中 Role 名称为 `agentcube-router`\n660: - [ ] `rbac/router.yaml` 中 RoleBinding 名称为 `agentcube-router-binding`\n661: - [ ] `rbac-router.yaml` 已删除\n662: - [ ] `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 存在且包含 SA/CR/CRB\n663: - [ ] `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 中 ClusterRole 名称为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`\n664: - [ ] `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 中 ClusterRoleBinding 名称为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`\n665: - [ ] `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 仅含 ConfigMap/Service/Deployment\n666: - [ ] 所有 RBAC 资源包含 `app.kubernetes.io/name`, `app.kubernetes.io/instance`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` 标签\n667: - [ ] WM ClusterRole 规则集与变更前一致 (13 条规则)\n668: - [ ] Router Role 规则集与变更前一致 (secrets 全权限)\n669: - [ ] Volcano ClusterRole 规则集与变更前一致 (18 条规则)\n670: - [ ] 所有 Binding 的 roleRef 和 subjects 引用正确\n671: - [ ] `--set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false` 不渲染 WM RBAC 资源\n672: - [ ] `--set router.rbac.create=true` 渲染 Router RBAC 资源\n673: - [ ] `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 渲染 Volcano 全套资源 (RBAC + 非 RBAC)\n674: - [ ] `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` 仅渲染 Volcano 非 RBAC 资源\n675: \n676: ---\n677: \n678: ## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n679: \n680: | 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n681: |------|----------|------|\n682: | agentd 组件 RBAC | 依赖本 AR 完成 | agentd (空闲清理控制器) 需要独立的 SA/Role/RoleBinding，遵循本 AR 建立的命名和标签规范 |\n683: | picod 组件 RBAC | 依赖本 AR 完成 | picod (sandbox 内执行守护进程) 需要独立的 SA/Role，遵循本 AR 建立的命名和标签规范 |\n684: | NetworkPolicy 配置 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 为各组件添加 NetworkPolicy 资源，限制 Pod 间网络通信 |\n685: | PodSecurityStandards 集成 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 为 namespace 添加 Pod Security Standards 标签 (restricted/baseline/privileged) |\n686: | OPA/Gatekeeper 策略 | 独立 | 外部策略引擎集成，验证 RBAC 权限不超过最小权限原则 |\n687: | Kyverno 策略 | 独立 | 外部策略引擎集成，自动校验和修补 RBAC 资源配置 |\n688: | Helm RBAC 单元测试 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 引入 helm-unittest 插件，将 delta-spec 场景转为自动化测试用例 |\n689: | RBAC 权限审计工具 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 自动化对比变更前后的权限规则集，确保无意外增减 |\n\n(End of file - total 689 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n本变更统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中（`rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`、`rbac-router.yaml`、`volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`），命名风格不一致，且 Volcano 调度器的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。\n\n本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。这是 RBAC 配置的基础设施重构，不改变任何权限范围。\n\n### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n\n**当前状态 (Before):**\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/\n├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service\n├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service\n├── rbac/\n│   └── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (无 values gate)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md","time":{"start":1775873498737,"end":1775873498745}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775873500115,"sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4f1f00001GD2MkCPGxX1UFz","messageID":"msg_d7a4f063f001W7RCLVNxolgQCs","sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_fa0ba14b2ebb401aaabf1dac","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `manifests`\n6: - **Language:** YAML\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: RBAC directory consolidation\n13: \n14: All RBAC resources SHALL be defined under `templates/rbac/` directory. The file `rbac-router.yaml` SHALL be moved to `templates/rbac/router.yaml`. The Volcano scheduler RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) SHALL be extracted from `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` into `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`. The original `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` SHALL retain only non-RBAC resources (ConfigMap, Service, Deployment).\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: RBAC files are in the correct directory\n17: - **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/templates/`\n18: - **WHEN** the directory listing is inspected\n19: - **THEN** `rbac/` contains `workloadmanager.yaml`, `router.yaml`, and `volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n20: - **AND** `rbac-router.yaml` no longer exists at the templates root\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: Volcano template retains only non-RBAC resources\n23: - **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: true`\n24: - **WHEN** `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` is rendered\n25: - **THEN** the output contains ConfigMap, Service, and Deployment for the Volcano scheduler\n26: - **AND** no ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, or ClusterRoleBinding appears from this template\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC renders from the new location\n29: - **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: true`\n30: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n31: - **THEN** the output contains ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and ClusterRoleBinding for the Volcano scheduler from `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ### Requirement: WorkloadManager RBAC values gate\n36: \n37: A new `values.yaml` key `workloadmanager.rbac.create` SHALL control whether WorkloadManager RBAC resources are rendered. The default SHALL be `true` to maintain backward compatibility. The template `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL be wrapped in a conditional `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}`.\n38: \n39: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager RBAC enabled by default\n40: - **GIVEN** default `values.yaml` (no explicit `workloadmanager.rbac.create` set)\n41: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n42: - **THEN** the output contains ServiceAccount `workloadmanager`, ClusterRole `workloadmanager`, and ClusterRoleBinding `workloadmanager`\n43: \n44: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager RBAC explicitly disabled\n45: - **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false`\n46: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n47: - **THEN** no WorkloadManager ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, or ClusterRoleBinding appears in the output\n48: \n49: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager RBAC explicitly enabled\n50: - **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.rbac.create=true`\n51: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n52: - **THEN** the output contains all three WorkloadManager RBAC resources\n53: \n54: ---\n55: \n56: ### Requirement: Volcano scheduler RBAC values gate\n57: \n58: A new `values.yaml` key `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` SHALL control whether Volcano scheduler RBAC resources are rendered. When the value is empty string `\"\"` (default), it SHALL follow `volcano.scheduler.enabled`. When set explicitly to `true` or `false`, it SHALL override the enabled flag. The template `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` SHALL use the conditional logic: `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.rbac.create | default .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}`.\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC follows enabled by default\n61: - **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: false` and `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` unset (empty)\n62: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n63: - **THEN** no Volcano scheduler RBAC resources appear\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC follows enabled when true\n66: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` and `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` unset\n67: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n68: - **THEN** the output contains Volcano scheduler ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and ClusterRoleBinding\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC explicitly disabled regardless of enabled\n71: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false`\n72: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n73: - **THEN** no Volcano scheduler RBAC resources appear in the output\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC explicitly enabled regardless of disabled\n76: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true`\n77: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n78: - **THEN** the output contains Volcano scheduler ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and ClusterRoleBinding\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ### Requirement: Router RBAC gate unchanged\n83: \n84: The existing `router.rbac.create` gate (default `false`) SHALL remain unchanged in behavior. The Router RBAC template moved to `templates/rbac/router.yaml` SHALL preserve the same conditional rendering logic.\n85: \n86: #### Scenario: Router RBAC off by default after move\n87: - **GIVEN** default values after the file move\n88: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n89: - **THEN** no Router ServiceAccount, Role, or RoleBinding appears\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: Router RBAC enabled after move\n92: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n93: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n94: - **THEN** the output contains Router ServiceAccount, Role, and RoleBinding with the same names and rules as before the move\n95: \n96: ---\n97: \n98: ### Requirement: ClusterRole naming with agentcube- prefix\n99: \n100: All ClusterRole resources SHALL be named with the `agentcube-` prefix to avoid cluster-wide naming conflicts. The naming convention SHALL be `agentcube-<component>`. This applies to WorkloadManager and Volcano scheduler ClusterRoles.\n101: \n102: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRole has agentcube- prefix\n103: - **GIVEN** default values\n104: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n105: - **THEN** the WorkloadManager ClusterRole is named `agentcube-workloadmanager`\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: Volcano ClusterRole has agentcube- prefix\n108: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n109: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n110: - **THEN** the Volcano scheduler ClusterRole is named `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: ClusterRoleBinding references the prefixed ClusterRole name\n113: - **GIVEN** default values\n114: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n115: - **THEN** `ClusterRoleBinding/agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` has `roleRef.name: agentcube-workloadmanager`\n116: \n117: ---\n118: \n119: ### Requirement: ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding naming with -binding suffix\n120: \n121: All ClusterRoleBinding and RoleBinding resources SHALL be named with the `-binding` suffix. The naming convention SHALL be `agentcube-<component>-binding`. This applies to WorkloadManager, Router, and Volcano scheduler bindings.\n122: \n123: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager binding has -binding suffix\n124: - **GIVEN** default values\n125: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n126: - **THEN** the WorkloadManager ClusterRoleBinding is named `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`\n127: \n128: #### Scenario: Router binding has -binding suffix\n129: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n130: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n131: - **THEN** the Router RoleBinding is named `agentcube-router-binding`\n132: \n133: #### Scenario: Volcano binding has -binding suffix\n134: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n135: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n136: - **THEN** the Volcano scheduler ClusterRoleBinding is named `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`\n137: \n138: ---\n139: \n140: ### Requirement: ServiceAccount naming consistency\n141: \n142: ServiceAccount names SHALL remain consistent with their corresponding Deployment names. WorkloadManager SA stays as `workloadmanager`. Router SA stays as `agentcube-router` (or custom `router.serviceAccountName`). Volcano scheduler SA stays as `volcano-agent-scheduler`.\n143: \n144: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager SA name unchanged\n145: - **GIVEN** default values\n146: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n147: - **THEN** the ServiceAccount is named `workloadmanager`\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: Router SA respects serviceAccountName value\n150: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa`\n151: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n152: - **THEN** the Router ServiceAccount is named `my-router-sa`\n153: \n154: #### Scenario: Volcano SA name unchanged\n155: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n156: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n157: - **THEN** the Volcano scheduler ServiceAccount is named `volcano-agent-scheduler`\n158: \n159: ---\n160: \n161: ### Requirement: RBAC permissions unchanged\n162: \n163: No apiGroups, resources, or verbs SHALL be added, removed, or modified from any existing RBAC rule. The permission scope of WorkloadManager, Router, and Volcano scheduler roles SHALL be identical before and after this change (only names and file locations change).\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRole rules preserved\n166: - **GIVEN** default values\n167: - **WHEN** the rendered ClusterRole `agentcube-workloadmanager` is inspected\n168: - **THEN** it contains the exact same rules as the original `ClusterRole/workloadmanager`:\n169:   - `agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes` with full CRUD\n170:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`, `sandboxtemplates`, `sandboxwarmpools` with full CRUD\n171:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status` with `get,update,patch`\n172:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters` with full CRUD\n173:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/status` with `get,update,patch`\n174:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/finalizers` with `update`\n175:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes` with `get,list,watch`\n176:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes/status` with `update,patch`\n177:   - core `pods` with `get,list,watch`\n178:   - core `secrets` with full CRUD\n179:   - `authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews` with `create`\n180: \n181: #### Scenario: Router Role rules preserved\n182: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n183: - **WHEN** the rendered Role is inspected\n184: - **THEN** it grants `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` on `secrets` in the release namespace (unchanged)\n185: \n186: #### Scenario: Volcano ClusterRole rules preserved\n187: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n188: - **WHEN** the rendered ClusterRole `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` is inspected\n189: - **THEN** it contains the exact same rules as the original `ClusterRole/volcano-agent-scheduler` (CRDs, pods, nodes, storage, scheduling, leases, resourceclaims, nodeshards, etc.)\n190: \n191: ---\n192: \n193: ### Requirement: Kubernetes standard labels on RBAC resources\n194: \n195: All RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, Role, ClusterRoleBinding, RoleBinding) SHALL include the labels `app.kubernetes.io/name`, `app.kubernetes.io/instance`, and `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`. The `app.kubernetes.io/name` value SHALL match the component name (e.g., `workloadmanager`, `router`, `volcano-scheduler`). These labels SHALL be applied via the `agentcube.labels` helper combined with the component-specific label.\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager RBAC has kubernetes standard labels\n198: - **GIVEN** default values and release name `my-release`\n199: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n200: - **THEN** the WorkloadManager ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and ClusterRoleBinding each have labels:\n201:   - `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager`\n202:   - `app.kubernetes.io/instance: my-release`\n203:   - `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n204: \n205: #### Scenario: Router RBAC has kubernetes standard labels\n206: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true` and release name `my-release`\n207: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n208: - **THEN** the Router ServiceAccount, Role, and RoleBinding each have labels:\n209:   - `app.kubernetes.io/name: router`\n210:   - `app.kubernetes.io/instance: my-release`\n211:   - `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n212: \n213: #### Scenario: Volcano RBAC has kubernetes standard labels\n214: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` and release name `my-release`\n215: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n216: - **THEN** the Volcano scheduler ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and ClusterRoleBinding each have labels:\n217:   - `app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-scheduler`\n218:   - `app.kubernetes.io/instance: my-release`\n219:   - `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n220: \n221: ---\n222: \n223: ### Requirement: _helpers.tpl RBAC name helpers\n224: \n225: The `_helpers.tpl` file SHALL define two new template helpers:\n226: - `agentcube.rbacName` — returns `agentcube-<component>` for ClusterRole/Role naming\n227: - `agentcube.rbacBindingName` — returns `agentcube-<component>-binding` for ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding naming\n228: \n229: Both helpers SHALL accept a component name as a parameter and truncate to 63 characters with trailing `-` trimmed.\n230: \n231: #### Scenario: rbacName helper generates prefixed name\n232: - **GIVEN** the helper `agentcube.rbacName` is called with component `workloadmanager`\n233: - **WHEN** the template is rendered\n234: - **THEN** it returns `agentcube-workloadmanager`\n235: \n236: #### Scenario: rbacBindingName helper generates binding name\n237: - **GIVEN** the helper `agentcube.rbacBindingName` is called with component `workloadmanager`\n238: - **WHEN** the template is rendered\n239: - **THEN** it returns `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`\n240: \n241: #### Scenario: Long component names are truncated\n242: - **GIVEN** the helper `agentcube.rbacName` is called with a component name that would exceed 63 characters when prefixed\n243: - **WHEN** the template is rendered\n244: - **THEN** the result is truncated to 63 characters with trailing `-` trimmed\n245: \n246: ---\n247: \n248: ### Requirement: values.yaml RBAC key tree\n249: \n250: The `values.yaml` SHALL include the following RBAC-related keys:\n251: - `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true` (new, default true)\n252: - `router.rbac.create: false` (existing, unchanged)\n253: - `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create: \"\"` (new, empty string to follow `enabled`)\n254: \n255: Comments SHALL document the purpose of each key and the default behavior.\n256: \n257: #### Scenario: values.yaml parses with new RBAC keys\n258: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\n259: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n260: - **THEN** `workloadmanager.rbac.create` exists and equals `true`\n261: - **AND** `router.rbac.create` exists and equals `false`\n262: - **AND** `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` exists and equals `\"\"` (empty string)\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: RBAC key comments document behavior\n265: - **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is read as text\n266: - **WHEN** the `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` key area is inspected\n267: - **THEN** a comment explains that empty string means the value follows `volcano.scheduler.enabled`\n268: \n269: ---\n270: \n271: ### Requirement: Helm upgrade backward compatibility\n272: \n273: An existing AgentCube release installed before this change SHALL upgrade without resource deletion or recreation of RBAC objects that would cause downtime. Helm's native resource tracking (by GVK + namespace + name) SHALL handle the file move and rename correctly.\n274: \n275: #### Scenario: Upgrade from pre-AR-031 release\n276: - **GIVEN** a release installed with the chart before RBAC consolidation (ClusterRole named `workloadmanager`, ClusterRoleBinding named `workloadmanager`)\n277: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with the post-AR-031 chart\n278: - **THEN** the old ClusterRole `workloadmanager` is deleted and new ClusterRole `agentcube-workloadmanager` is created\n279: - **AND** the old ClusterRoleBinding `workloadmanager` is deleted and new ClusterRoleBinding `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` is created\n280: - **AND** no WorkloadManager pods are restarted during the upgrade (only RBAC resources change)\n281: \n282: #### Scenario: Router RBAC file move is transparent\n283: - **GIVEN** a release with `router.rbac.create: true` installed before the file move\n284: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with the post-AR-031 chart\n285: - **THEN** Router RBAC resources are tracked by their GVK + name, not by template filename\n286: - **AND** no Router RBAC resources are deleted and recreated\n287: \n288: ---\n289: \n290: ### Requirement: RBAC resource binding integrity\n291: \n292: Each ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding SHALL correctly reference its corresponding ClusterRole/Role and ServiceAccount after the naming changes. The `roleRef` in bindings SHALL use the new prefixed ClusterRole/Role name, and `subjects` SHALL reference the correct ServiceAccount in the release namespace.\n293: \n294: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager binding integrity\n295: - **GIVEN** default values and release namespace `agentcube`\n296: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n297: - **THEN** `ClusterRoleBinding/agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` has:\n298:   - `roleRef.kind: ClusterRole`, `roleRef.name: agentcube-workloadmanager`\n299:   - `subjects[0].kind: ServiceAccount`, `subjects[0].name: workloadmanager`, `subjects[0].namespace: agentcube`\n300: \n301: #### Scenario: Router binding integrity\n302: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router` and release namespace `agentcube`\n303: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n304: - **THEN** `RoleBinding/agentcube-router-binding` has:\n305:   - `roleRef.kind: Role`, `roleRef.name: agentcube-router`\n306:   - `subjects[0].kind: ServiceAccount`, `subjects[0].name: agentcube-router`, `subjects[0].namespace: agentcube`\n307: \n308: #### Scenario: Volcano binding integrity\n309: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` and release namespace `agentcube`\n310: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n311: - **THEN** `ClusterRoleBinding/agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` has:\n312:   - `roleRef.kind: ClusterRole`, `roleRef.name: agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`\n313:   - `subjects[0].kind: ServiceAccount`, `subjects[0].name: volcano-agent-scheduler`, `subjects[0].namespace: agentcube`\n314: \n315: ---\n316: \n317: ### Requirement: Helm lint passes on RBAC templates\n318: \n319: All RBAC templates SHALL pass `helm lint` without errors or warnings related to RBAC resource definitions.\n320: \n321: #### Scenario: Lint passes with default values\n322: - **GIVEN** the chart at `manifests/charts/base`\n323: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\n324: - **THEN** no errors are reported\n325: - **AND** no warnings related to RBAC resources are reported\n326: \n327: #### Scenario: Lint passes with all RBAC enabled\n328: - **GIVEN** the chart at `manifests/charts/base`\n329: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` is run\n330: - **THEN** no errors are reported\n331: - **AND** no warnings related to RBAC resources are reported\n332: \n333: ---\n334: \n335: ## File Changes\n336: \n337: | Action | File | Description |\n338: |--------|------|-------------|\n339: | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Add `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true` and `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create: \"\"` keys |\n340: | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` | Add `agentcube.rbacName` and `agentcube.rbacBindingName` template helpers |\n341: | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Add `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}` gate; rename ClusterRole to `agentcube-workloadmanager`; rename ClusterRoleBinding to `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`; add `app.kubernetes.io/*` labels |\n342: | Rename | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` → `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/router.yaml` | Move into rbac/ directory; rename Role to `agentcube-router`; rename RoleBinding to `agentcube-router-binding`; add `app.kubernetes.io/*` labels |\n343: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` | Extract ServiceAccount/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding from volcano template; rename ClusterRole to `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`; rename ClusterRoleBinding to `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`; add `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` gate; add `app.kubernetes.io/*` labels |\n344: | Modify | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Remove ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding; retain ConfigMap, Service, Deployment only |\n\n(End of file - total 344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `manifests`\n- **Language:** YAML\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: RBAC directory consolidation\n\nAll RBAC resources SHALL be defined under `templates/rbac/` directory. The file `rbac-router.yaml` SHALL be moved to `templates/rbac/router.yaml`. The Volcano scheduler RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) SHALL be extracted from `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` into `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`. The original `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` SHALL retain only non-RBAC resources (ConfigMap, Service, Deployment).\n\n#### Scenario: RBAC files are in the correct directory\n- **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/templates/`\n- **WHEN** the directory listing is inspected\n- **THEN** `rbac/` contains `workloadmanager.yaml`, `router.yaml`, and `volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n- **AND** `rbac-router.yaml` no longer exists at the templates root","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775873500106,"end":1775873500113}}}}
