{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775873502724,"sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4f297b0014NmmxUUyQuRo9F","messageID":"msg_d7a4f063f001W7RCLVNxolgQCs","sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2b50b99a535b487e8d409dbc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** manifests\n4: > **Language:** YAML\n5: > **Size:** L\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-030/design.md`, `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** `make gen-crd` 已可用（或 CRD 手工编写）\n9: \n10: ---\n11: \n12: ## T-001: Chart.yaml 元数据\n13: \n14: - [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/`\n15: - [ ] T-001.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml`\n16: - [ ] T-001.03 设置 `apiVersion: v1`\n17: - [ ] T-001.04 设置 `name: agentcube`\n18: - [ ] T-001.05 设置 `description: A Helm chart for AgentCube`\n19: - [ ] T-001.06 设置 `version: 0.1.0`\n20: - [ ] T-001.07 设置 `appVersion: 1.0.0`\n21: \n22: **验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml')); assert d['apiVersion']=='v1' and d['name']=='agentcube' and d['version']=='0.1.0' and d['appVersion']=='1.0.0'\"` 无报错\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## T-002: values.yaml 默认值树\n27: \n28: - [ ] T-002.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\n29: - [ ] T-002.02 定义全局键 `imagePullSecrets: []`、`nameOverride: \"\"`、`fullnameOverride: \"\"`\n30: - [ ] T-002.03 定义 `redis.addr: \"\"` 和 `redis.password: \"\"`，含注释标明安装时必须通过 `--set` 提供\n31: - [ ] T-002.04 定义 `router` 完整键树：`replicas: 1`，`image.repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router`，`image.pullPolicy: IfNotPresent`，`image.tag: latest`，`service.type: ClusterIP`，`service.port: 8080`，`service.targetPort: 8080`，`resources.limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}`，`resources.requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}`，`config: {}`，`extraEnv: []`，`serviceAccountName: \"\"`，`rbac.create: false`\n32: - [ ] T-002.05 定义 `workloadmanager` 完整键树：`replicas: 1`，`image.repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager`，`image.pullPolicy: IfNotPresent`，`image.tag: latest`，`service.type: ClusterIP`，`service.port: 8080`，`resources.limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}`，`resources.requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}`，`extraEnv: []`\n33: - [ ] T-002.06 定义 `volcano.scheduler.enabled: false`，`volcano.scheduler.replicas: 1`，`volcano.scheduler.image.repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler`，`volcano.scheduler.image.pullPolicy: IfNotPresent`，`volcano.scheduler.image.tag: latest`\n34: \n35: **验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml')); assert all(k in d for k in ['imagePullSecrets','nameOverride','fullnameOverride','redis','router','workloadmanager','volcano'])\"` 无报错；`redis.addr == \"\"`；`volcano.scheduler.enabled == false`\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## T-003: CRD 文件 — AgentRuntime\n40: \n41: - [ ] T-003.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n42: - [ ] T-003.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n43: - [ ] T-003.03 CRD 名称为 `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n44: - [ ] T-003.04 API Group 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`，Version `v1alpha1`（served + storage）\n45: - [ ] T-003.05 Scope 为 `Namespaced`\n46: - [ ] T-003.06 注解 `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2`\n47: - [ ] T-003.07 PrinterColumn `Age`（date, `.metadata.creationTimestamp`）\n48: - [ ] T-003.08 Subresources 包含 `status`\n49: - [ ] T-003.09 spec.required 包含 `maxSessionDuration`、`podTemplate`、`sessionTimeout`、`targetPort`\n50: - [ ] T-003.10 spec 字段定义：`maxSessionDuration`（string duration, default `8h`）、`sessionTimeout`（string duration, default `15m`）、`targetPort`（array, required items `port`+`protocol` enum HTTP/HTTPS）、`podTemplate`（object PodSpec-shaped, required）\n51: \n52: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"` 有输出；CRD YAML 解析后 `spec.group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`；`spec.versions` 含 `v1alpha1` served+storage；`scope == \"Namespaced\"`\n53: \n54: ---\n55: \n56: ## T-004: CRD 文件 — CodeInterpreter\n57: \n58: - [ ] T-004.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`\n59: - [ ] T-004.02 CRD 名称为 `codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n60: - [ ] T-004.03 API Group 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`，Version `v1alpha1`（served + storage）\n61: - [ ] T-004.04 Scope 为 `Namespaced`\n62: - [ ] T-004.05 注解 `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2`\n63: - [ ] T-004.06 Subresources 包含 `status`\n64: - [ ] T-004.07 spec.required 包含 `template`\n65: - [ ] T-004.08 spec 字段定义：`authMode`（enum `picod|none`, default `picod`）、`maxSessionDuration`（string duration, default `8h`）、`sessionTimeout`（string duration, default `15m`）、`ports`（array TargetPort）、`template`（object: image, command, args, env, resources, runtimeClassName）、`warmPoolSize`（int32, optional）\n66: \n67: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"` 有输出；CRD YAML 解析后 `spec.group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`；`spec.authMode.default == \"picod\"`\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## T-005: Workload Manager Deployment + Service 模板\n72: \n73: - [ ] T-005.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/templates/`\n74: - [ ] T-005.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n75: - [ ] T-005.03 Deployment 名为 `workloadmanager`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n76: - [ ] T-005.04 `spec.replicas` 使用 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.replicas }}`\n77: - [ ] T-005.05 Selector 和 pod labels 包含 `app: workloadmanager`\n78: - [ ] T-005.06 容器名 `workloadmanager`，镜像 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.tag }}`\n79: - [ ] T-005.07 `imagePullPolicy` 使用 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy }}`\n80: - [ ] T-005.08 容器端口名 `http`，值为 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}`\n81: - [ ] T-005.09 环境变量 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 使用 `valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace`\n82: - [ ] T-005.10 环境变量 `REDIS_ADDR` 使用 `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}`\n83: - [ ] T-005.11 环境变量 `REDIS_PASSWORD` 使用 `{{ .Values.redis.password }}`\n84: - [ ] T-005.12 `extraEnv` 通过 `{{- range .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}` 注入\n85: - [ ] T-005.13 容器 args 包含 `--port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` 和 `--runtime-class-name=`\n86: - [ ] T-005.14 资源 requests/limits 从 values 读取\n87: - [ ] T-005.15 Liveness probe: HTTP GET `/health`，port 使用 service port，`initialDelaySeconds: 10`，`periodSeconds: 10`\n88: - [ ] T-005.16 Readiness probe: HTTP GET `/health`，port 使用 service port，`initialDelaySeconds: 5`，`periodSeconds: 5`\n89: - [ ] T-005.17 `serviceAccountName: workloadmanager`\n90: - [ ] T-005.18 `imagePullSecrets` 条件注入（`{{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}`）\n91: - [ ] T-005.19 Service 名为 `workloadmanager`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n92: - [ ] T-005.20 Service `type` 使用 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.type }}`，`port` 和 `targetPort` 使用 `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}`\n93: - [ ] T-005.21 Service selector `app: workloadmanager`\n94: \n95: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` 输出合法 YAML；包含 Deployment 和 Service；`replicas: 1`；`image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest`；liveness `/health` initialDelay 10s；readiness `/health` initialDelay 5s；env 含 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` fieldRef\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## T-006: Router Deployment + Service 模板\n100: \n101: - [ ] T-006.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n102: - [ ] T-006.02 Deployment 名为 `agentcube-router`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n103: - [ ] T-006.03 `spec.replicas` 使用 `{{ .Values.router.replicas }}`\n104: - [ ] T-006.04 Selector 和 pod labels 包含 `app: agentcube-router`\n105: - [ ] T-006.05 容器名 `agentcube-router`，镜像 `{{ .Values.router.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.router.image.tag }}`\n106: - [ ] T-006.06 `imagePullPolicy` 使用 `{{ .Values.router.image.pullPolicy }}`\n107: - [ ] T-006.07 容器端口值为 `{{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}`\n108: - [ ] T-006.08 环境变量 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 使用 `valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace`\n109: - [ ] T-006.09 环境变量 `REDIS_ADDR` 使用 `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}`\n110: - [ ] T-006.10 环境变量 `REDIS_PASSWORD` 使用 `{{ .Values.redis.password }}`\n111: - [ ] T-006.11 环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 值为 `http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}`\n112: - [ ] T-006.12 `extraEnv` 通过 `{{- range .Values.router.extraEnv }}` 注入\n113: - [ ] T-006.13 容器 args 包含 `--port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}` 和 `--debug`\n114: - [ ] T-006.14 资源 requests/limits 从 values 读取\n115: - [ ] T-006.15 Liveness probe: HTTP GET `/health/live`，port 使用 targetPort，`initialDelaySeconds: 1`，`periodSeconds: 2`\n116: - [ ] T-006.16 Readiness probe: HTTP GET `/health/ready`，port 使用 targetPort，`initialDelaySeconds: 1`，`periodSeconds: 2`\n117: - [ ] T-006.17 `serviceAccountName` 条件注入：`{{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}`\n118: - [ ] T-006.18 `imagePullSecrets` 条件注入\n119: - [ ] T-006.19 Service 名为 `agentcube-router`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n120: - [ ] T-006.20 Service `type` 使用 `{{ .Values.router.service.type }}`，`port` 使用 `{{ .Values.router.service.port }}`，`targetPort` 使用 `{{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}`\n121: - [ ] T-006.21 Service selector `app: agentcube-router`\n122: \n123: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/agentcube-router.yaml --namespace agentcube` 输出含 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080`；liveness `/health/live` initialDelay 1s；readiness `/health/ready` initialDelay 1s；args 含 `--port=8080` 和 `--debug`\n124: \n125: ---\n126: \n127: ## T-007: Workload Manager RBAC 模板\n128: \n129: - [ ] T-007.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/`\n130: - [ ] T-007.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\n131: - [ ] T-007.03 ServiceAccount 名为 `workloadmanager`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n132: - [ ] T-007.04 ClusterRole 名为 `workloadmanager`\n133: - [ ] T-007.05 ClusterRole 规则：`agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n134: - [ ] T-007.06 ClusterRole 规则：`extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n135: - [ ] T-007.07 ClusterRole 规则：`extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n136: - [ ] T-007.08 ClusterRole 规则：`extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n137: - [ ] T-007.09 ClusterRole 规则：`extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status` → `get,update,patch`\n138: - [ ] T-007.10 ClusterRole 规则：`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n139: - [ ] T-007.11 ClusterRole 规则：`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/status` → `get,update,patch`\n140: - [ ] T-007.12 ClusterRole 规则：`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/finalizers` → `update`\n141: - [ ] T-007.13 ClusterRole 规则：`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes` → `get,list,watch`\n142: - [ ] T-007.14 ClusterRole 规则：`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes/status` → `update,patch`\n143: - [ ] T-007.15 ClusterRole 规则：`\"\"/pods` → `get,list,watch`\n144: - [ ] T-007.16 ClusterRole 规则：`\"\"/secrets` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n145: - [ ] T-007.17 ClusterRole 规则：`authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews` → `create`\n146: - [ ] T-007.18 ClusterRoleBinding 名为 `workloadmanager`\n147: - [ ] T-007.19 ClusterRoleBinding subject: ServiceAccount `workloadmanager`，namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n148: - [ ] T-007.20 ClusterRoleBinding roleRef: ClusterRole `workloadmanager`，apiGroup `rbac.authorization.k8s.io`\n149: \n150: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 输出含 SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding；ClusterRole 包含全部 13 条规则；ClusterRoleBinding subject 和 roleRef 正确\n151: \n152: ---\n153: \n154: ## T-008: Router RBAC 模板（条件渲染）\n155: \n156: - [ ] T-008.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml`\n157: - [ ] T-008.02 整个文件包裹在 `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}` / `{{- end }}` 中\n158: - [ ] T-008.03 ServiceAccount 名为 `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n159: - [ ] T-008.04 Role 名与 SA 同名，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n160: - [ ] T-008.05 Role 规则：`\"\"/secrets` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n161: - [ ] T-008.06 RoleBinding 名与 SA 同名，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n162: - [ ] T-008.07 RoleBinding subject: ServiceAccount（同名），namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n163: - [ ] T-008.08 RoleBinding roleRef: Role（同名），apiGroup `rbac.authorization.k8s.io`\n164: \n165: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无 Router RBAC 输出；`helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true` 输出含 SA + Role + RoleBinding，均名为 `agentcube-router`；`--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa` 输出资源名为 `my-router-sa`\n166: \n167: ---\n168: \n169: ## T-009: Volcano Agent Scheduler 模板（条件渲染）\n170: \n171: - [ ] T-009.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`\n172: - [ ] T-009.02 整个文件包裹在 `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` / `{{- end }}` 中\n173: - [ ] T-009.03 ServiceAccount 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n174: - [ ] T-009.04 ConfigMap 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n175: - [ ] T-009.05 ConfigMap data `agent-scheduler.conf` 包含 `actions: \"allocate\"` 和 tiers with `predicates` + `nodeorder`\n176: - [ ] T-009.06 ClusterRole 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler`，包含 design.md 2.5.3 节定义的全部规则集（apiextensions.k8s.io CRDs、events、pods、pods/status、pods/binding、PVCs、PVs、namespaces/services/replicationcontrollers、resourcequotas、nodes、storage.k8s.io、policy PDBs、scheduling.k8s.io priorityclasses、volcano podgroups、configmaps、apps daemonsets/replicasets/statefulsets、coordination.k8s.io leases、resource.k8s.io resourceclaims/deviceclasses/resourceslices、shard.volcano.sh nodeshards）\n177: - [ ] T-009.07 ClusterRoleBinding 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler-role`\n178: - [ ] T-009.08 ClusterRoleBinding subject: ServiceAccount `volcano-agent-scheduler`，namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n179: - [ ] T-009.09 ClusterRoleBinding roleRef: ClusterRole `volcano-agent-scheduler`\n180: - [ ] T-009.10 Service 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler-service`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n181: - [ ] T-009.11 Service port `8080`，含 Prometheus metrics annotations\n182: - [ ] T-009.12 Service selector `app: volcano-agent-scheduler`\n183: - [ ] T-009.13 Deployment 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler`，namespace 使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n184: - [ ] T-009.14 `spec.replicas` 使用 `{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.replicas }}`\n185: - [ ] T-009.15 Selector 和 pod labels 包含 `app: volcano-agent-scheduler`\n186: - [ ] T-009.16 容器镜像 `{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.tag }}`\n187: - [ ] T-009.17 容器 args 包含 `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler`\n188: - [ ] T-009.18 容器端口 `8080`\n189: - [ ] T-009.19 环境变量 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 使用 `valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace`\n190: - [ ] T-009.20 Volume mount ConfigMap `volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap`\n191: - [ ] T-009.21 Volume emptyDir（如设计需要）\n192: - [ ] T-009.22 Security contexts（如设计需要）\n193: \n194: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无 Volcano 输出；`helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 输出含 SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment；ConfigMap 含 `agent-scheduler.conf` with `allocate`/`predicates`/`nodeorder`；Deployment replicas 和 image 匹配 values；Service 含 prometheus annotations\n195: \n196: ---\n197: \n198: ## T-010: _helpers.tpl 命名辅助函数\n199: \n200: - [ ] T-010.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n201: - [ ] T-010.02 定义 `agentcube.fullname` 辅助函数：优先使用 `fullnameOverride`，否则使用 `{{ .Release.Name }}-{{ .Chart.Name }}`，截断 63 字符并 trim 尾部 `-`\n202: - [ ] T-010.03 定义 `agentcube.name` 辅助函数：使用 `nameOverride` 或 `.Chart.Name`\n203: \n204: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set fullnameOverride=agentcube-prod` 渲染出的资源名称使用 `agentcube-prod` 前缀；`helm template test manifests/charts/base` 使用默认命名\n205: \n206: ---\n207: \n208: ## T-011: Helm Lint 与模板渲染验证\n209: \n210: - [ ] T-011.01 运行 `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors\n211: - [ ] T-011.02 运行 `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 输出合法 YAML\n212: - [ ] T-011.03 验证默认渲染输出含 2 个 Deployment（workloadmanager + agentcube-router）\n213: - [ ] T-011.04 验证默认渲染输出含 2 个 Service\n214: - [ ] T-011.05 验证默认渲染输出含 1 个 ClusterRole（workloadmanager）\n215: - [ ] T-011.06 验证默认渲染输出含 1 个 ServiceAccount（workloadmanager）\n216: - [ ] T-011.07 验证默认渲染输出无 Router RBAC 资源\n217: - [ ] T-011.08 验证默认渲染输出无 Volcano 资源\n218: \n219: **验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: Deployment\"` 输出 2；`grep -c \"kind: Service\"` 输出 2；`grep -c \"kind: ClusterRole\"` 输出 1；`grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\"` 输出 1\n220: \n221: ---\n222: \n223: ## T-012: 场景化模板渲染测试\n224: \n225: - [ ] T-012.01 测试 `--set redis.addr=redis.ns:6379 --set redis.password=secret` → WM 和 Router env 含 `REDIS_ADDR` 和 `REDIS_PASSWORD`\n226: - [ ] T-012.02 测试 `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3` → WM Deployment `replicas: 3`\n227: - [ ] T-012.03 测试 `--set workloadmanager.image.repository=myregistry/wm --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.2.3` → WM 容器镜像 `myregistry/wm:v1.2.3`\n228: - [ ] T-012.04 测试 `--set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM\",\"value\":\"val\"}]'` → WM env 含 `CUSTOM: val`\n229: - [ ] T-012.05 测试 `--set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` → 所有 Deployment 含 `imagePullSecrets`\n230: - [ ] T-012.06 测试 `--namespace production` → 所有命名空间资源 `namespace: production`\n231: - [ ] T-012.07 测试 `--set router.rbac.create=true` → Router SA + Role + RoleBinding 出现\n232: - [ ] T-012.08 测试 `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` → Volcano SA + ConfigMap + CR + CRB + Service + Deployment 出现\n233: - [ ] T-012.09 测试 `--set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router` → Router Deployment 含 `serviceAccountName: agentcube-router`\n234: - [ ] T-012.10 测试默认 `router.serviceAccountName=\"\"` → Router Deployment 不含 `serviceAccountName` 字段\n235: - [ ] T-012.11 测试 `--set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"debug\"}]'` → Router env 含 `LOG_LEVEL: debug`\n236: - [ ] T-012.12 测试 `--set workloadmanager.service.type=NodePort` → WM Service `type: NodePort`\n237: \n238: **验收**: 每个场景的 `helm template` 输出通过 grep/assert 验证预期内容存在\n239: \n240: ---\n241: \n242: ## T-013: CRD 渲染验证\n243: \n244: - [ ] T-013.01 `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"kind: CustomResourceDefinition\"` 输出 2 行\n245: - [ ] T-013.02 AgentRuntime CRD 名称 `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` 存在于输出\n246: - [ ] T-013.03 CodeInterpreter CRD 名称 `codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` 存在于输出\n247: - [ ] T-013.04 两个 CRD 的 `spec.group` 均为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n248: - [ ] T-013.05 两个 CRD 的 `scope` 均为 `Namespaced`\n249: \n250: **验收**: 以上 grep/assert 全部通过\n251: \n252: ---\n253: \n254: ## T-014: kubectl dry-run 验证\n255: \n256: - [ ] T-014.01 `helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n257: - [ ] T-014.02 `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=redis.ns.svc:6379 --set redis.password=secret --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set router.rbac.create=true | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n258: \n259: **验收**: 两次 dry-run 均无错误输出\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ## T-015: nameOverride / fullnameOverride 验证\n264: \n265: - [ ] T-015.01 测试默认命名：`helm template my-release manifests/charts/base` → 资源使用默认名称（`workloadmanager`、`agentcube-router`）\n266: - [ ] T-015.02 测试 `--set fullnameOverride=agentcube-prod` → 适用资源名称使用 `agentcube-prod` 前缀\n267: - [ ] T-015.03 测试 `--set nameOverride=ac` → 适用资源名称使用 `my-release-ac` 前缀\n268: \n269: **验收**: 渲染输出中资源名称符合预期命名模式\n270: \n271: ---\n272: \n273: ## Dependency Graph\n274: \n275: ```\n276: T-001 (Chart.yaml) ──┬── T-002 (values.yaml) ──┬── T-005 (WM template) ──┐\n277:                       │                         ├── T-006 (Router template)┤\n278:                       │                         ├── T-008 (Router RBAC)   ├── T-011 (Lint + render)\n279:                       │                         └── T-009 (Volcano)       │\n280:                       ├── T-003 (AgentRuntime CRD)                        ├── T-012 (Scenario tests)\n281:                       │                                                   ├── T-013 (CRD verify)\n282:                       └── T-010 (_helpers.tpl) ───────────────────────────┘\n283:                                                                     ├── T-014 (dry-run)\n284:                                                                     └── T-015 (naming)\n285: ```\n286: \n287: ## Parallelizable Groups\n288: \n289: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n290: |-------|-------|---------------|\n291: | G1 | T-001 (Chart.yaml), T-002 (values.yaml) | None |\n292: | G2 | T-003 (AgentRuntime CRD), T-004 (CodeInterpreter CRD) | G1 (目录存在) 或 `make gen-crd` |\n293: | G3 | T-005 (WM template), T-006 (Router template) | G1 (values.yaml 结构确定) |\n294: | G4 | T-007 (WM RBAC), T-008 (Router RBAC), T-009 (Volcano), T-010 (_helpers.tpl) | G1 |\n295: | G5 | T-011 (Lint + render), T-012 (Scenario tests), T-013 (CRD verify) | G2 + G3 + G4 |\n296: | G6 | T-014 (dry-run), T-015 (naming) | G5 |\n297: \n298: ---\n299: \n300: ## Acceptance Criteria\n301: \n302: | # | Criterion | Command |\n303: |---|-----------|---------|\n304: | AC1 | Chart.yaml metadata correct | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml')); assert d['apiVersion']=='v1' and d['name']=='agentcube' and d['version']=='0.1.0' and d['appVersion']=='1.0.0'\"` |\n305: | AC2 | values.yaml valid YAML with all top-level keys | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml')); assert all(k in d for k in ['imagePullSecrets','nameOverride','fullnameOverride','redis','router','workloadmanager','volcano'])\"` |\n306: | AC3 | Redis defaults empty with install-time comments | values.yaml 中 `redis.addr: \"\"` 和 `redis.password: \"\"` 含注释标明必填 |\n307: | AC4 | Helm lint passes | `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors |\n308: | AC5 | Default template renders 2 Deployments, 2 Services, 1 ClusterRole, 1 SA | `helm template test manifests/charts/base \\| grep -c \"kind: Deployment\"` → 2 |\n309: | AC6 | WM Deployment: replicas, image, probes, env, args, resources, SA | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` 验证全部字段 |\n310: | AC7 | WM Service: type, port, selector | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` 验证 Service 部分 |\n311: | AC8 | Router Deployment: replicas, image, probes, env (含 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL), args, conditional SA | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/agentcube-router.yaml --namespace agentcube` |\n312: | AC9 | Router Service: type, port, targetPort, selector | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/agentcube-router.yaml` 验证 Service 部分 |\n313: | AC10 | WM RBAC: SA + ClusterRole (13 rules) + ClusterRoleBinding | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` |\n314: | AC11 | Router RBAC off by default | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无 Router RBAC |\n315: | AC12 | Router RBAC enabled with custom SA name | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-sa` |\n316: | AC13 | Volcano disabled by default | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无 Volcano 资源 |\n317: | AC14 | Volcano enabled: SA + ConfigMap + CR + CRB + Service + Deployment | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` |\n318: | AC15 | CRDs present with correct group/version/scope | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds \\| grep \"kind: CustomResourceDefinition\"` → 2 |\n319: | AC16 | Namespace scoping via Release.Namespace | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --namespace production` 所有命名空间资源 `namespace: production` |\n320: | AC17 | imagePullSecrets applied | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` |\n321: | AC18 | kubectl dry-run passes (default + full overrides) | `helm template test manifests/charts/base \\| kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无错误 |\n322: | AC19 | fullnameOverride renames resources | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set fullnameOverride=agentcube-prod` |\n\n(End of file - total 322 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** manifests\n> **Language:** YAML\n> **Size:** L\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-030/design.md`, `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** `make gen-crd` 已可用（或 CRD 手工编写）\n\n---\n\n## T-001: Chart.yaml 元数据\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/`\n- [ ] T-001.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml`\n- [ ] T-001.03 设置 `apiVersion: v1`\n- [ ] T-001.04 设置 `name: agentcube`\n- [ ] T-001.05 设置 `description: A Helm chart for AgentCube`\n- [ ] T-001.06 设置 `version: 0.1.0`\n- [ ] T-001.07 设置 `appVersion: 1.0.0`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/op