{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775873696744,"sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a4fab38001JhuU0XyZYNiW7Z","messageID":"msg_d7a4f84b6001TReCIr0KzHWftJ","sessionID":"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_2c3ac5cd5ceb448a8a5631ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** manifests\n> **Language:** YAML\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-031/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-031/design.md`, `changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** AR-030 (Helm Chart 模板与 Values) 基线已就位\n\n---\n\n## T-001: values.yaml 新增 RBAC 控制键\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 在 `workloadmanager` 下添加 `rbac.create: true`，含注释说明默认开启以保持向后兼容\n- [ ] T-001.02 在 `volcano.scheduler` 下添加 `rbac.create: \"\"`，含注释说明空字符串表示跟随 `enabled`\n- [ ] T-001.03 确认 `router.rbac.create: false` 已存在且保持不变\n\n**验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml')); assert d['workloadmanager']['rbac']['create']==True; assert d['volcano']['scheduler']['rbac']['create']==''; assert d['router']['rbac']['create']==False\"` 无报错\n\n---\n\n## T-002: _helpers.tpl 新增 RBAC 命名辅助函数\n\n- [ ] T-002.01 定义 `agentcube.rbacName` helper：输入组件名，输出 `agentcube-<component>`，截断 63 字符并 trim 尾部 `-`\n- [ ] T-002.02 定义 `agentcube.rbacBindingName` helper：输入组件名，输出 `agentcube-<component>-binding`，截断 63 字符并 trim 尾部 `-`\n- [ ] T-002.03 两个 helper 均包含注释文档（用途、输入、输出）\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无模板渲染错误；helper 定义语法正确\n\n---\n\n## T-003: WorkloadManager RBAC 模板改造\n\n- [ ] T-003.01 在文件顶部添加 `{{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"workloadmanager\" }}`\n- [ ] T-003.02 整个文件包裹在 `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}` / `{{- end }}` 中\n- [ ] T-003.03 ServiceAccount labels 替换为 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-003.04 ClusterRole 名称改为 `{{ include \"agentcube.rbacName\" \"workloadmanager\" }}`（渲染为 `agentcube-workloadmanager`）\n- [ ] T-003.05 ClusterRole labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-003.06 ClusterRole 规则集保持 13 条不变（apiGroups/resources/verbs 完全一致）\n- [ ] T-003.07 ClusterRoleBinding 名称改为 `{{ include \"agentcube.rbacBindingName\" \"workloadmanager\" }}`（渲染为 `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`）\n- [ ] T-003.08 ClusterRoleBinding labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-003.09 ClusterRoleBinding roleRef.name 改为 `{{ include \"agentcube.rbacName\" \"workloadmanager\" }}`\n- [ ] T-003.10 ClusterRoleBinding subjects 保持不变（ServiceAccount `workloadmanager`, namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`）\n- [ ] T-003.11 移除旧的 `app: workloadmanager` 简单标签\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 输出含 SA + ClusterRole(`agentcube-workloadmanager`) + ClusterRoleBinding(`agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`)；三个资源均含 `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager`、`app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`、`app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`；ClusterRole 含 13 条规则；`--set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false` 无输出\n\n---\n\n## T-004: Router RBAC 模板迁移与改造\n\n- [ ] T-004.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/router.yaml`\n- [ ] T-004.02 在文件顶部添加 `{{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"router\" }}`\n- [ ] T-004.03 条件 gate 保持 `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}` / `{{- end }}`\n- [ ] T-004.04 ServiceAccount 名称保持 `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}`\n- [ ] T-004.05 ServiceAccount labels 替换为 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: router` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-004.06 Role 名称改为固定 `agentcube-router`（不再跟随 `serviceAccountName`）\n- [ ] T-004.07 Role labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: router` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-004.08 Role 规则保持：`\"\"/secrets` → `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n- [ ] T-004.09 RoleBinding 名称改为固定 `agentcube-router-binding`\n- [ ] T-004.10 RoleBinding labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: router` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-004.11 RoleBinding roleRef 改为固定 `kind: Role`, `name: agentcube-router`\n- [ ] T-004.12 RoleBinding subjects 保持引用 `{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}`\n- [ ] T-004.13 移除旧的 `app: agentcube-router` 简单标签\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 无 Router RBAC 输出；`--set router.rbac.create=true` 输出含 SA(`agentcube-router`) + Role(`agentcube-router`) + RoleBinding(`agentcube-router-binding`)；`--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa` → SA 名为 `my-router-sa`，Role/RB 名仍为 `agentcube-router`/`agentcube-router-binding`\n\n---\n\n## T-005: 删除旧 Router RBAC 模板文件\n\n- [ ] T-005.01 删除 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml`\n\n**验收**: `ls manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` 返回文件不存在\n\n---\n\n## T-006: Volcano Scheduler RBAC 模板抽取\n\n- [ ] T-006.01 创建 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n- [ ] T-006.02 在文件顶部添加 `{{- $_ := set . \"componentName\" \"volcano-scheduler\" }}`\n- [ ] T-006.03 条件 gate 使用 `{{- if or .Values.volcano.scheduler.rbac.create .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` / `{{- end }}`\n- [ ] T-006.04 ServiceAccount 名为 `volcano-agent-scheduler`，namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n- [ ] T-006.05 ServiceAccount labels 使用 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-scheduler` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-006.06 ClusterRole 名称改为 `{{ include \"agentcube.rbacName\" \"volcano-agent-scheduler\" }}`（渲染为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`）\n- [ ] T-006.07 ClusterRole labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-scheduler` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-006.08 ClusterRole 规则集保持 18 条不变（从原 volcano 模板完整迁移，apiGroups/resources/verbs 完全一致）\n- [ ] T-006.09 ClusterRoleBinding 名称改为 `{{ include \"agentcube.rbacBindingName\" \"volcano-agent-scheduler\" }}`（渲染为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`）\n- [ ] T-006.10 ClusterRoleBinding labels 添加 `{{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-scheduler` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-006.11 ClusterRoleBinding roleRef 改为 `kind: ClusterRole`, `name: {{ include \"agentcube.rbacName\" \"volcano-agent-scheduler\" }}`\n- [ ] T-006.12 ClusterRoleBinding subjects 保持引用 ServiceAccount `volcano-agent-scheduler`, namespace `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 输出含 SA(`volcano-agent-scheduler`) + ClusterRole(`agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`) + ClusterRoleBinding(`agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`)；ClusterRole 含 18 条规则；`--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` 无输出；`--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true` 有输出\n\n---\n\n## T-007: Volcano 主模板剥离 RBAC 资源\n\n- [ ] T-007.01 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中删除 ServiceAccount 块（第 2-8 行）\n- [ ] T-007.02 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中删除 ClusterRole 块（第 25-215 行）\n- [ ] T-007.03 从 `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 中删除 ClusterRoleBinding 块（第 217-228 行）\n- [ ] T-007.04 保留 ConfigMap、Service、Deployment 块及其 `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` gate\n- [ ] T-007.05 确认 Deployment 的 `serviceAccountName: volcano-agent-scheduler` 引用与新 RBAC 模板创建的 SA 名称一致\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 仅输出 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment，无 SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding\n\n---\n\n## T-008: Helm Lint 验证\n\n- [ ] T-008.01 `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors\n- [ ] T-008.02 `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 无 errors\n\n**验收**: 两次 lint 均无 `[ERROR]` 输出\n\n---\n\n## T-009: 默认值模板渲染验证\n\n- [ ] T-009.01 `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 输出合法 YAML\n- [ ] T-009.02 默认渲染含 1 个 ClusterRole（`agentcube-workloadmanager`）\n- [ ] T-009.03 默认渲染含 1 个 ClusterRoleBinding（`agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`）\n- [ ] T-009.04 默认渲染含 1 个 ServiceAccount（`workloadmanager`）\n- [ ] T-009.05 默认渲染无 Router RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-009.06 默认渲染无 Volcano RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-009.07 默认渲染无 `rbac-router.yaml` 相关输出\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: ClusterRole\"` → 1；`grep -c \"kind: ClusterRoleBinding\"` → 1；`grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\"` → 1；`grep \"agentcube-workloadmanager\"` 有输出；`grep \"agentcube-router\"` 无输出；`grep \"volcano-agent-scheduler\"` 无 RBAC 相关输出\n\n---\n\n## T-010: 全量 RBAC 启用场景渲染验证\n\n- [ ] T-010.01 `--set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 渲染出全部 3 套 RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-010.02 WM RBAC：SA `workloadmanager` + CR `agentcube-workloadmanager` + CRB `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`\n- [ ] T-010.03 Router RBAC：SA `agentcube-router` + Role `agentcube-router` + RoleBinding `agentcube-router-binding`\n- [ ] T-010.04 Volcano RBAC：SA `volcano-agent-scheduler` + CR `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` + CRB `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`\n- [ ] T-010.05 Volcano 非 RBAC 资源（ConfigMap + Service + Deployment）同时渲染\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 输出含上述全部资源名称\n\n---\n\n## T-011: RBAC 条件门控场景验证\n\n- [ ] T-011.01 `--set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false` → 无 WM RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-011.02 `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` → 有 Volcano 非 RBAC 资源，无 Volcano RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-011.03 `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true` → 仅有 Volcano RBAC 资源，无非 RBAC 资源\n- [ ] T-011.04 `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa` → SA 名为 `my-router-sa`，Role/RB 名仍为 `agentcube-router`/`agentcube-router-binding`\n\n**验收**: 每个场景的 `helm template` 输出通过 grep 验证预期资源存在/不存在\n\n---\n\n## T-012: 标签一致性验证\n\n- [ ] T-012.01 WM RBAC 三个资源均含 `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager`、`app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`、`app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-012.02 Router RBAC 三个资源均含 `app.kubernetes.io/name: router`、`app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`、`app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-012.03 Volcano RBAC 三个资源均含 `app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-scheduler`、`app.kubernetes.io/instance: test`、`app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\n- [ ] T-012.04 所有 RBAC 资源均含 `helm.sh/chart`、`app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: Helm` 标签\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml | grep -A 6 \"labels:\"` 验证 WM 标签；`--set router.rbac.create=true -s templates/rbac/router.yaml` 验证 Router 标签；`--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 验证 Volcano 标签\n\n---\n\n## T-013: 绑定完整性验证\n\n- [ ] T-013.01 WM ClusterRoleBinding roleRef.name = `agentcube-workloadmanager`，subjects[0].name = `workloadmanager`\n- [ ] T-013.02 Router RoleBinding roleRef.name = `agentcube-router`，subjects[0].name = `agentcube-router`（默认）或自定义 SA 名\n- [ ] T-013.03 Volcano ClusterRoleBinding roleRef.name = `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`，subjects[0].name = `volcano-agent-scheduler`\n- [ ] T-013.04 所有 Binding 的 subjects[0].namespace = `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`（渲染后为 release 命名空间）\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml | grep -A 10 \"kind: ClusterRoleBinding\"` 验证 WM 绑定；`--set router.rbac.create=true -s templates/rbac/router.yaml` 验证 Router 绑定；`--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` 验证 Volcano 绑定\n\n---\n\n## T-014: 权限规则不变验证\n\n- [ ] T-014.01 WM ClusterRole 规则数 = 13 条（与原 `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` 一致）\n- [ ] T-014.02 Router Role 规则 = `\"\"/secrets` 全权限（与原一致）\n- [ ] T-014.03 Volcano ClusterRole 规则数 = 18 条（与原 `ClusterRole/volcano-agent-scheduler` 一致）\n\n**验收**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml | python3 -c \"import yaml,sys; docs=[d for d in yaml.safe_load_all(sys.stdin) if d and d['kind']=='ClusterRole']; rules=docs[0]['rules']; assert len(rules)==13, f'Expected 13 rules, got {len(rules)}'\"`；类似验证 Router(1 rule) 和 Volcano(18 rules)\n\n---\n\n## T-015: kubectl dry-run 验证\n\n- [ ] T-015.01 `helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n- [ ] T-015.02 `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n\n**验收**: 两次 dry-run 均无错误输出\n\n---\n\n## T-016: 目录结构最终验证\n\n- [ ] T-016.01 `templates/rbac/` 目录包含 `workloadmanager.yaml`、`router.yaml`、`volcano-scheduler.yaml`\n- [ ] T-016.02 `templates/rbac-router.yaml` 不存在\n- [ ] T-016.03 `templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` 仅含 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment\n\n**验收**: `ls manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/` 输出三个文件；`test ! -f manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` 返回 0；`helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true -s templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml | grep \"kind:\"` 仅输出 ConfigMap、Service、Deployment\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n```\nT-001 (values.yaml) ──┬── T-002 (_helpers.tpl) ──┬── T-003 (WM RBAC) ──┐\n                       │                          ├── T-004 (Router RBAC)├── T-005 (delete old)\n                       │                          └── T-006 (Volcano RBAC)\n                       │                                             │\n                       └──────────────────────────────────────────────┴── T-007 (Volcano strip)\n                                                                        │\n                                                    ┌───────────────────┘\n                                                    │\n        T-008 (Lint) ───────────────────────────────┤\n        T-009 (Default render) ─────────────────────┤\n        T-010 (Full RBAC render) ───────────────────┤\n        T-011 (Conditional gates) ──────────────────┤\n        T-012 (Labels) ─────────────────────────────┤\n        T-013 (Binding integrity) ──────────────────┤\n        T-014 (Permission rules) ───────────────────┤\n        T-015 (dry-run) ────────────────────────────┤\n        T-016 (Directory structure) ────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Parallelizable Groups\n\n| Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n|-------|-------|---------------|\n| G1 | T-001 (values.yaml) | None |\n| G2 | T-002 (_helpers.tpl) | G1 |\n| G3 | T-003 (WM RBAC), T-004 (Router RBAC), T-006 (Volcano RBAC) | G2 |\n| G4 | T-005 (delete old), T-007 (Volcano strip) | G3 |\n| G5 | T-008–T-016 (全部验证) | G4 |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Command |\n|---|-----------|---------|\n| AC1 | values.yaml 含三个 RBAC 键且值正确 | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml')); assert d['workloadmanager']['rbac']['create']==True and d['volcano']['scheduler']['rbac']['create']=='' and d['router']['rbac']['create']==False\"` |\n| AC2 | _helpers.tpl 含 rbacName 和 rbacBindingName | `grep -c \"agentcube.rbacName\\|agentcube.rbacBindingName\" manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` → 2 |\n| AC3 | RBAC 文件位于 `templates/rbac/` 目录 | `ls manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/` 含 `workloadmanager.yaml router.yaml volcano-scheduler.yaml` |\n| AC4 | `rbac-router.yaml` 已删除 | `test ! -f manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` |\n| AC5 | WM ClusterRole 名为 `agentcube-workloadmanager` | `helm template test manifests/charts/base \\| grep \"name: agentcube-workloadmanager\"` |\n| AC6 | WM ClusterRoleBinding 名为 `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | `helm template test manifests/charts/base \\| grep \"name: agentcube-workloadmanager-binding\"` |\n| AC7 | Router Role 名为 `agentcube-router`（固定） | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true \\| grep \"name: agentcube-router\"` |\n| AC8 | Router RoleBinding 名为 `agentcube-router-binding` | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true \\| grep \"name: agentcube-router-binding\"` |\n| AC9 | Volcano ClusterRole 名为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\| grep \"name: agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler\"` |\n| AC10 | Volcano ClusterRoleBinding 名为 `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\| grep \"name: agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding\"` |\n| AC11 | WM RBAC 默认开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 有输出 |\n| AC12 | WM RBAC 可关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.rbac.create=false -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` 无输出 |\n| AC13 | Volcano RBAC 跟随 enabled | `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 有 RBAC 输出；默认无 |\n| AC14 | Volcano RBAC 可独立关闭 | `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=false` 无 RBAC 输出 |\n| AC15 | Volcano RBAC 可独立开启 | `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=false --set volcano.scheduler.rbac.create=true` 有 RBAC 输出 |\n| AC16 | 所有 RBAC 资源含 k8s 标准标签 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml \\| grep \"app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\"` |\n| AC17 | WM ClusterRole 13 条规则不变 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml \\| python3 -c \"import yaml,sys; docs=[d for d in yaml.safe_load_all(sys.stdin) if d and d['kind']=='ClusterRole']; assert len(docs[0]['rules'])==13\"` |\n| AC18